500341,112,2204,2,14,1,91,10,Āsāvatī nāma {latā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto purāṇadutiyikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
500342,112,2204,15,29,1,35,4,Vatthu indriyajātake( jā.1.8.60 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
500343,112,2204,30,99,1,338,45,"Idha pana satthā taṃ bhikkhuṃ‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ kena ukkaṇṭhāpitosī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ purāṇadutiyikāya, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhu esā itthī tuyhaṃ anatthakārikā, pubbepi tvaṃ etaṃ nissāya caturaṅginisenaṃ jahitvā himavantapadese mahantaṃ dukkhaṃ anubhavanto tīṇi saṃvaccharāni vasī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
500344,112,2205,2,25,1,228,22,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsigāme brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ uggahitasippo isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā vanamūlaphalāhāro abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā himavantapadese vasi. 
500345,112,2205,26,50,1,208,23,"Tasmiṃ kāle eko puññasampanno satto tāvatiṃsabhavanato cavitvā tasmiṃ ṭhāne padumasare ekasmiṃ padumagabbhe dārikā hutvā nibbatti, sesapadumesu purāṇabhāvaṃ patvā patantesupi taṃ mahākucchikaṃ hutvā tiṭṭhateva. "
500346,112,2205,51,90,1,265,34,"Tāpaso nahāyituṃ padumasaraṃ gato taṃ disvā‘‘ aññesu padumesu patantesupi idaṃ mahākucchikaṃ hutvā tiṭṭhati, kiṃ nu kho kāraṇan’’ ti cintetvā udakasāṭakaṃ nivāsetvā otaranto gantvā taṃ padumaṃ vivaritvā taṃ dārikaṃ disvā dhītusaññaṃ uppādetvā paṇṇasālaṃ ānetvā paṭijaggi. "
500347,112,2205,91,103,1,107,11,"Sā aparabhāge soḷasavassikā hutvā abhirūpā ahosi uttamarūpadharā atikkantā mānusakavaṇṇaṃ, apattā devavaṇṇaṃ. "
500348,112,2205,104,134,1,145,21,"Tadā sakko bodhisattassa upaṭṭhānaṃ āgacchati, so taṃ dārikaṃ disvā‘‘ kuto esā’’ ti pucchitvā laddhaniyāmaṃ sutvā‘‘ imissā kiṃ laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti pucchi."
