500444,112,2245,2,15,1,81,11,Na me {ruccī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ dubbacabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
500445,112,2245,16,66,1,259,35,"Satthā taṃ bhikkhuṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu dubbaco’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ āma, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ na kho bhikkhu idāneva, pubbepi tvaṃ dubbacoyeva, dubbacabhāvañca pana nissāya paṇḍitānaṃ vacanaṃ akaronto verambhavātamukhe byasanaṃ gatosī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
500446,112,2246,2,14,1,107,11,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto gijjhayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā apanandagijjho nāma ahosi. 
500447,112,2246,15,19,1,44,4,So gijjhagaṇaparivuto gijjhakūṭapabbate vasi. 
500448,112,2246,20,34,1,106,13,"Putto panassa migālopo nāma thāmabalasampanno ahosi, so aññesaṃ gijjhānaṃ sīmaṃ atikkamitvā atiuccaṃ uppati. "
500449,112,2246,35,47,1,59,8,Gijjhā‘‘ putto te atidūraṃ uppatatī’’ ti gijjharañño ācikkhiṃsu. 
500450,112,2246,48,73,1,123,17,"So taṃ pakkosetvā‘‘ tvaṃ kira, tāta, atiuccaṃ gacchasi, atiuccaṃ gacchanto jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇissasī’’ ti vatvā tisso gāthā abhāsi– "
