500494,112,2275,35,69,1,256,28,"Athekadivasaṃ so cintesi‘‘ sace mayā suciparivārasīlo koci āgamissati, tassa mama nisīdanapallaṅkaṃ vā nipajjanasayanaṃ vā dātuṃ na yuttaṃ, anucchiṭṭhaṃ aparibhuttaṃ dātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti attano vasanaṭṭhāneyeva ekapasse aparibhuttapallaṅkañca senāsanañca paññāpesi. "
