500701,112,2399,2,7,1,24,2,[ 384]9. Dhammadhajajātakavaṇṇanā 
500702,112,2400,2,14,1,91,11,Dhammaṃ caratha {ñātayo}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kuhakabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
500703,112,2400,15,36,1,88,14,"Tadā hi satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, ayaṃ idāneva kuhako, pubbepi kuhakoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
500704,112,2401,2,15,1,139,13,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto sakuṇayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā vayappatto sakuṇasaṅghaparivuto samuddamajjhe dīpake vasi. 
500705,112,2401,16,28,1,106,11,"Athekacce kāsiraṭṭhavāsino vāṇijā disākākaṃ gahetvā nāvāya samuddaṃ pakkhandiṃsu, samuddamajjhe nāvā bhijji. "
500706,112,2401,29,56,1,148,21,"So disākāko taṃ dīpakaṃ gantvā cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ mahāsakuṇasaṅgho, mayā kuhakakammaṃ katvā etesaṃ aṇḍakāni ceva chāpake ca varaṃ varaṃ khādituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
500707,112,2401,57,67,1,83,10,So otaritvā sakuṇasaṅghassa majjhe mukhaṃ vivaritvā ekena pādena pathaviyaṃ aṭṭhāsi.
500708,112,2401,68,89,1,62,12,"‘‘ Ko nāma tvaṃ, sāmī’’ ti sakuṇehi puṭṭho‘‘ ahaṃ dhammiko nāmā’’ ti āha."
