500713,112,2401,141,162,1,107,16,"Evañca pana vatvā te sakuṇe āmantetvā‘‘ ovādaṃ vo dassāmi, taṃ suṇāthā’’ ti tesaṃ ovādavasena paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
500714,112,2402,2,4,1,0,0,65.
