500719,112,2405,15,32,1,104,14,"Dhammaṃ caratha bhaddaṃ {vo}ti ekavāraṃ caritvā mā osakkatha, punappunaṃ caratha, evaṃ bhaddaṃ vo bhavissati. "
500720,112,2405,33,50,1,123,14,"Sukhaṃ {setī}ti desanāsīsametaṃ, dhammacārī pana sukhaṃ tiṭṭhati gacchati nisīdati seti, sabbiriyāpathesu sukhito hotīti dīpeti. "
