501005,112,2535,2,13,1,52,8,"Tayā ca maṃ nimanteyya, yañcatthaññaṃ ghare dhanan’’ ti. "
501006,112,2536,2,7,1,38,5,Tattha sūcin ti vibhattivipallāso kato. 
501007,112,2536,8,19,1,85,10,Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– sūci nāma pajānatā paṇḍitena purisena kammāragāmasmiṃyeva vikketabbā. 
501008,112,2536,20,21,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
501009,112,2536,22,57,1,275,31,"Ācariyāva jānanti, kammaṃ sukatadukkaṭan ti, tassa tassa sippassa ācariyāva tasmiṃ tasmiṃ sippe sukatadukkaṭakammaṃ jānanti, svāhaṃ kammārakammaṃ ajānantānaṃ gahapatikānaṃ gāmaṃ gantvā mama sūciyā sukatadukkaṭabhāvaṃ kathaṃ jānāpessāmi, imasmiṃ pana gāme mama balaṃ jānāpessāmīti. "
501010,112,2536,58,65,1,50,7,Evaṃ bodhisatto imāya gāthāya attano balaṃ vaṇṇesi. 
501011,112,2537,2,48,1,192,34,"Tayā ca maṃ {nimanteyyā}ti bhadde sace tava pitā imaṃ mayā kataṃ sūciṃ‘‘ īdisā vā esā, evaṃ vā katā’’ ti jāneyya,‘‘ imaṃ me dhītaraṃ tava pādaparicārikaṃ dammi, gaṇhāhi nan’’ ti evaṃ tayā ca maṃ nimanteyya. "
501012,112,2537,49,66,1,111,16,"Yañcatthaññaṃ ghare dhanan ti yañca aññaṃ saviññāṇakaṃ vā aviññāṇakaṃ vā ghare dhanaṃ atthi, tena maṃ nimanteyya."
501013,112,2537,67,82,1,68,10,"‘‘ Yañcassaññan’’ tipi pāṭho, yañca assa ghare aññaṃ dhanaṃ atthīti attho. "
