501033,112,2538,239,276,1,180,25,Puna tena‘‘ ayaṃ maññe sūcī’’ ti vutto‘‘ ayampi sūcikosakoyevā’’ ti vatvā nakhena paharanto paṭipāṭiyā cha sūcikosake kammārajeṭṭhakassa pādamūle ṭhapetvā‘‘ ayaṃ sūcī’’ ti tassa hatthe ṭhapesi. 
501034,112,2538,277,283,1,56,5,"Kammārasahassāni aṅguliyo phoṭesuṃ, celukkhepā pavattiṃsu. "
