501044,112,2541,2,4,1,24,2,Sūcijātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
501045,112,2543,2,7,1,20,2,[ 388]3. Tuṇḍilajātakavaṇṇanā 
501046,112,2544,2,14,1,90,10,{Navachannake}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ maraṇabhīrukaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
501047,112,2544,15,40,1,235,24,"So kira sāvatthivāsī kulaputto buddhasāsane pabbajitvā maraṇabhīruko ahosi, appamattakampi sākhācalanaṃ daṇḍakapatanaṃ sakuṇacatuppadasaddaṃ vā aññaṃ vā tathārūpaṃ sutvā maraṇabhayatajjito hutvā kucchiyaṃ viddhasaso viya kampanto vicari. "
501048,112,2544,41,75,1,222,26,"Bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, asuko kira bhikkhu maraṇabhīruko appamattakampi saddaṃ sutvā vikampamāno palāyati, imesañca sattānaṃ maraṇameva dhuvaṃ, jīvitaṃ addhuvaṃ, nanu tadeva yoniso manasi kātabban’’ ti. "
501049,112,2544,76,140,1,270,38,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte taṃ bhikkhuṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu maraṇabhīruko’’ ti vatvā‘‘ āma, bhante’’ ti tena paṭiññāto‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa maraṇabhīrukoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
501050,112,2545,2,12,1,92,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto sūkariyā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
501051,112,2545,13,18,1,38,5,Sūkarī pariṇatagabbhā dve putte vijāyi. 
501052,112,2545,19,26,1,46,7,Sā ekadivasaṃ te gahetvā ekasmiṃ āvāṭe nipajji. 
501053,112,2545,27,39,1,117,11,Athekā bārāṇasidvāragāmavāsinī mahallikā kappāsakhettato pacchipuṇṇaṃ kappāsaṃ ādāya yaṭṭhiyā bhūmiṃ ākoṭentī āgacchi. 
501054,112,2545,40,48,1,62,8,Sūkarī taṃ saddaṃ sutvā maraṇabhayena puttake chaḍḍetvā palāyi. 
501055,112,2545,49,69,1,175,19,"Mahallikā sūkarapotake disvā puttasaññaṃ paṭilabhitvā pacchiyaṃ pakkhipitvā gharaṃ netvā jeṭṭhakassa mahātuṇḍilo, kaniṭṭhassa cūḷatuṇḍiloti nāmaṃ karitvā te puttake viya posesi. "
501056,112,2545,70,76,1,42,5,Te aparabhāge vaḍḍhitvā thūlasarīrā ahesuṃ. 
501057,112,2545,77,99,1,77,14,Mahallikā‘‘ ime no mūlena dehī’’ ti vuccamānāpi‘‘ puttā me’’ ti vatvā kassaci na deti. 
501058,112,2545,100,141,1,220,32,"Athekasmiṃ chaṇakāle dhuttā suraṃ pivantā maṃse khīṇe‘‘ kuto nu kho maṃsaṃ labhissāmā’’ ti vīmaṃsantā mahallikāya gehe sūkarānaṃ atthibhāvaṃ ñatvā mūlaṃ gahetvā tattha gantvā‘‘ amma, mūlaṃ gahetvā ekaṃ no sūkaraṃ dehī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
501059,112,2545,142,165,1,103,16,"Sā‘‘ alaṃ, tātā, puttā me ete, puttaṃ nāma maṃsaṃ khādanatthāya kiṇantānaṃ dadantā nāma natthī’’ ti paṭikkhipi. "
501060,112,2545,166,209,1,222,31,"Dhuttā‘‘ amma, manussānaṃ sūkarā nāma puttā na honti, dehi no’’ ti punappunaṃ yācantāpi alabhitvā mahallikaṃ suraṃ pāyetvā mattakāle‘‘ amma, sūkarehi kiṃ karissasi, mūlaṃ gahetvā paribbayaṃ karohī’’ ti tassā hatthe kahāpaṇe ṭhapayiṃsu. "
501061,112,2546,2,13,1,54,8,"Sā kahāpaṇe gahetvā‘‘ tātā, mahātuṇḍilaṃ dātuṃ na sakkomi. "
501062,112,2546,14,22,1,33,5,Cūḷatuṇḍilaṃ pana gaṇhathā’’ ti āha.
501063,112,2546,23,30,1,11,3,‘‘ Kahaṃ so’’ ti?
501064,112,2546,31,42,1,40,6,"‘‘ Ayaṃ etasmiṃ gaccheti, saddamassa dehī’’ ti."
501065,112,2546,43,51,1,20,4,‘‘ Āhāraṃ na passāmī’’ ti. 
501066,112,2546,52,57,1,41,5,Dhuttā mūlena ekaṃ bhattapātiṃ āharāpesuṃ. 
501067,112,2546,58,67,1,75,9,Mahallikā taṃ gahetvā dvāre ṭhapitaṃ sūkaradoṇiṃ pūretvā doṇisamīpe aṭṭhāsi. 
501068,112,2546,68,73,1,48,5,Tiṃsamattāpi dhuttā pāsahatthā tattheva aṭṭhaṃsu. 
501069,112,2546,74,87,1,51,7,"Mahallikā‘‘ tāta, cūḷatuṇḍila, ehī’’ ti tassa saddamakāsi. "
501070,112,2546,88,117,1,167,22,"Taṃ sutvā mahātuṇḍilo‘‘ ettakaṃ kālaṃ mama mātarā cūḷatuṇḍilassa saddo na dinnapubbo, maṃyeva paṭhamaṃ saddāyati, avassaṃ ajja amhākaṃ bhayaṃ uppannaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti aññāsi. "
501071,112,2546,118,136,1,72,12,"So kaniṭṭhaṃ āmantesi‘‘ tāta, mama mātā taṃ pakkosati, gaccha tāva jānāhī’’ ti. "
501072,112,2546,137,164,1,194,22,"So gacchā nikkhamitvā bhattadoṇisamīpe tesaṃ ṭhitabhāvaṃ disvā‘‘ ajja me maraṇaṃ uppannan’’ ti maraṇabhayatajjito nivattitvā kampamāno bhātu santikaṃ āgantvā thambhituṃ nāsakkhi, kampamāno paribbhami. "
