501265,112,2643,2,14,1,84,10,Sakuṇo mayhako {nāmā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto āgantukaseṭṭhiṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
501266,112,2643,15,21,1,56,6,Sāvatthiyañhi āgantukaseṭṭhi nāma aḍḍho ahosi mahaddhano. 
501267,112,2643,22,69,1,369,40,"So neva attanā bhoge bhuñji, na paresaṃ adāsi, nānaggarase paṇīte bhojane upanīte taṃ na bhuñjati, bilaṅgadutiyaṃ kaṇājakaṃ eva bhuñjati, dhūpitavāsitesu kāsikavatthesu upanītesu tāni hāretvā thūlathūlasāṭake nivāseti, ājānīyayutte maṇikanakavicitte rathe upanīte tampi harāpetvā kattararathakena gacchati, suvaṇṇacchatte dhāriyamāne taṃ apanetvā paṇṇacchattena dhāriyamānena. "
501268,112,2643,70,80,1,77,10,So yāvajīvaṃ dānādīsu puññesu ekampi akatvā kālaṃ katvā roruvaniraye nibbatti. 
501269,112,2643,81,89,1,77,8,Tassa aputtakaṃ sāpateyyaṃ rājabalaṃ sattahi rattidivasehi rājakulaṃ pavesesi. 
501270,112,2643,90,175,1,559,67,"Tasmiṃ pavesite rājā bhuttapātarāso jetavanaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā nisinno‘‘ kiṃ, mahārāja, buddhupaṭṭhānaṃ na karosī’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhante, sāvatthiyaṃ āgantukaseṭṭhino nāma kālakatassa assāmikadhane amhākaṃ ghare āhariyamāneyeva satta rattidivasā gatā, so pana etaṃ dhanaṃ labhitvāpi neva attanā paribhuñji, na paresaṃ adāsi, rakkhasapariggahitapokkharaṇī viyassa dhanaṃ ahosi, so ekadivasampi paṇītabhojanādīnaṃ rasaṃ ananubhavitvāva maraṇamukhaṃ paviṭṭho, evaṃ maccharī apuññasatto kiṃ katvā ettakaṃ dhanaṃ labhi, kena cassa bhogesu cittaṃ na ramī’’ ti satthāraṃ pucchi. "
501271,112,2643,176,197,1,113,15,"Satthā‘‘ mahārāja, dhanalābho ca, dhanaṃ laddhā aparibhuñjanakāraṇañca teneva katan’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
501272,112,2644,2,20,1,125,16,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bārāṇasiseṭṭhi assaddho ahosi maccharī, na kassaci kiñci deti, na kañci saṅgaṇhāti. "
501273,112,2644,21,74,1,297,37,"So ekadivasaṃ rājupaṭṭhānaṃ gacchanto tagarasikhiṃ nāma paccekabuddhaṃ piṇḍāya carantaṃ disvā vanditvā‘‘ laddhā, bhante, bhikkhā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ nanu carāma mahāseṭṭhī’’ ti vutte purisaṃ āṇāpesi‘‘ gaccha, imaṃ amhākaṃ gharaṃ ānetvā mama pallaṅke nisīdāpetvā amhākaṃ paṭiyattabhattassa pattaṃ pūretvā dāpehī’’ ti. "
501274,112,2644,75,82,1,66,7,So paccekabuddhaṃ gharaṃ netvā nisīdāpetvā seṭṭhibhariyāya ācikkhi. 
501275,112,2644,83,89,1,50,6,Sā nānaggarasabhattassa pattaṃ pūretvā tassa adāsi. 
501276,112,2644,90,97,1,70,7,So bhattaṃ gahetvā seṭṭhinivesanā nikkhamitvā antaravīthiyaṃ paṭipajji. 
501277,112,2644,98,115,1,84,11,"Seṭṭhi rājakulato paccāgacchanto taṃ disvā vanditvā‘‘ laddhaṃ, bhante, bhattan’’ ti pucchi."
501278,112,2644,116,123,1,21,3,‘‘ Laddhaṃ mahāseṭṭhī’’ ti. 
501279,112,2644,124,157,1,177,26,"So pattaṃ oloketvā cittaṃ pasādetuṃ nāsakkhi ,‘‘ imaṃ me bhattaṃ dāsā vā kammakarā vā bhuñjitvā dukkarampi kammaṃ kareyyuṃ, aho vata me jānī’’ ti aparacetanaṃ paripuṇṇaṃ kātuṃ nāsakkhi. "
501280,112,2644,158,167,1,73,9,Dānañhi nāma tisso cetanā paripuṇṇaṃ kātuṃ sakkontasseva mahapphalaṃ hoti.
501281,112,2645,2,13,1,55,9,"‘ ‘ Pubbeva dānā sumanā bhavāma, dadampi ve attamanā bhavāma; "
501282,112,2646,2,22,1,61,9,"Datvāpi ve nānutappāma pacchā, tasmā hi amhaṃ daharā namiyyare.( jā.1.10.95);"
