501285,112,2649,2,21,1,163,16,"Iti , mahārāja, āgantukaseṭṭhi tagarasikhipaccekabuddhassa dinnapaccayena bahuṃ dhanaṃ labhi, datvā aparacetanaṃ paṇītaṃ kātuṃ asamatthatāya bhoge bhuñjituṃ nāsakkhīti."
501286,112,2649,22,34,1,36,7,"‘‘ Puttaṃ pana kasmā na labhi, bhante’’ ti? "
501287,112,2649,35,52,1,89,12,"Satthā‘‘ puttassa alabhanakāraṇampi teneva kataṃ, mahārājā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
501288,112,2650,2,26,1,235,23,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto asītikoṭivibhave seṭṭhikule nibbattitvā vayappatto mātāpitūnaṃ accayena kaniṭṭhaṃ saṅgaṇhitvā kuṭumbaṃ vicārento gharadvāre dānasālaṃ kāretvā mahādānaṃ pavattento agāraṃ ajjhāvasi. 
501289,112,2650,27,31,1,22,4,Athassa eko putto jāyi. 
501290,112,2650,32,67,1,260,30,So tassa padasā gamanakāle kāmesu ādīnavaṃ nekkhamme cānisaṃsaṃ disvā saddhiṃ puttadārena sabbaṃ gharavibhavaṃ kaniṭṭhassa niyyātetvā‘‘ appamatto dānaṃ pavattehī’’ ti ovādaṃ datvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā himavantapadese vihāsi. 
501291,112,2650,68,72,1,35,4,Kaniṭṭhopissa ekaṃ puttaṃ paṭilabhi. 
501292,112,2650,73,95,1,119,17,"So taṃ vaḍḍhantaṃ disvā cintesi‘‘ mama bhātu putte jīvante kuṭumbaṃ bhinditvā dvidhā bhavissati, bhātu puttaṃ māressāmī’’ ti. "
501293,112,2650,96,102,1,45,6,Atha naṃ ekadivasaṃ nadiyaṃ opilāpetvā māresi. 
501294,112,2650,103,117,1,59,10,Tamenaṃ nhatvā āgataṃ bhātu jāyā‘‘ kuhiṃ mama putto’’ ti pucchi.
