502741,112,3404,64,127,1,342,50,"Rājā te sakuṇe disvā cintesi‘‘ yo yo maṃsapesiṃ gaṇhi, tassa tasseva dukkhaṃ, yo yo taṃ vissajjesi, tassa tasseva sukhaṃ, imepi pañca kāmaguṇe yo yo gaṇhāti, tassa tasseva dukkhaṃ, itarassa sukhaṃ, ime hi bahūnaṃ sādhāraṇā, mayhaṃ kho pana soḷasa itthisahassāni, mayā vissaṭṭhamaṃsapiṇḍena viya senena pañca kāmaguṇe pahāya sukhitena bhavituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
