503072,112,3563,2,12,1,85,10,Ahaṃ dasasataṃbyāman ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kilesaniggahaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
503073,112,3563,13,28,1,39,5,Vatthu pana pānīyajātake( jā.1.11.59 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
503074,112,3563,29,88,1,438,49,"Idhāpi satthā antokoṭisanthāre kāmavitakkābhibhūte pañcasate bhikkhū disvā bhikkhusaṅghaṃ sannipātāpetvā‘‘ bhikkhave, āsaṅkitabbayuttakaṃ nāma āsaṅkituṃ vaṭṭati, kilesā nāma vaḍḍhantā vane nigrodhādayo viya rukkhaṃ, purisaṃ bhañjanti, teneva pubbepi koṭasimbaliyaṃ nibbattadevatā ekaṃ sakuṇaṃ nigrodhabījāni khāditvā attano rukkhassa sākhantare vaccaṃ pātentaṃ disvā‘ ito me vimānassa vināso bhavissatī’ ti bhayappattā ahosī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
503075,112,3564,2,12,1,98,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto koṭasimbaliyaṃ rukkhadevatā hutvā nibbatti. 
503076,112,3564,13,36,1,238,22,Atheko supaṇṇarājā diyaḍḍhayojanasatikaṃ attabhāvaṃ māpetvā pakkhavātehi mahāsamudde udakaṃ dvidhā katvā ekaṃ byāmasahassāyāmaṃ nāgarājānaṃ naṅguṭṭhe gahetvā mukhenassa gahitagocaraṃ chaḍḍāpetvā koṭasimbaliṃ sandhāya vanamatthakena pāyāsi. 
503077,112,3564,37,52,1,96,11,Nāgarājā‘‘ olambento attānaṃ mocessāmī’’ ti nigrodharukkhe bhogaṃ pavesetvā nigrodhaṃ veṭhetvā gaṇhi. 
503078,112,3564,53,61,1,90,8,Supaṇṇarañño mahābalatāya nāgarājassa ca mahāsarīratāya nigrodharukkho samugghāṭaṃ agamāsi. 
503079,112,3564,62,85,1,219,21,"Nāgarājā neva rukkhaṃ vissajjesi, supaṇṇarājā saddhiṃ nigrodharukkhena nāgarājānaṃ gahetvā koṭasimbaliṃ patvā nāgarājānaṃ khandhapiṭṭhe nipajjāpetvā udaramassa phāletvā nāgamedaṃ khāditvā sesakaḷevaraṃ samudde vissajjesi. "
