503194,112,3626,44,80,1,219,32,"Evaṃ yo saṃ {niraṃkatvā}ti evaṃ mahārāja, yo sakaṃ porāṇaṃ ajjhattikaṃ janaṃ nīharitvā pahāya kismiñci agaṇetvā āgantukaṃ piyaṃ karoti, so tumhādiso eko bahu socati, ayaṃ te mayā dassito dhūmakārī brāhmaṇo viya bahu socatīti. "
