503261,112,3667,14,34,1,206,20,Sā hi sāvatthiyaṃ ekassa mālākārajeṭṭhakassa dhītā uttamarūpadharā mahāpuññā soḷasavassikakāle ekadivasaṃ kumārikāhi saddhiṃ pupphārāmaṃ gacchantī tayo kummāsapiṇḍe gahetvā pupphapacchiyaṃ ṭhapetvā gacchati. 
503262,112,3667,35,48,1,140,13,Sā nagarato nikkhamanakāle bhagavantaṃ sarīrappabhaṃ vissajjetvā bhikkhusaṅghaparivutaṃ nagaraṃ pavisantaṃ disvā tayo kummāsapiṇḍe upanāmesi. 
