503565,112,3800,2,7,1,20,2,[ 417]1. Kaccānijātakavaṇṇanā 
503566,112,3801,2,18,1,105,12,Odātavatthā suci {allakesā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ mātuposakaṃ upāsakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
503567,112,3801,19,34,1,183,15,So kira sāvatthiyaṃ kuladārako ācārasampanno pitari kālakate mātudevato hutvā mukhadhovanadantakaṭṭhadānanhāpanapādadhovanādiveyyāvaccakammena ceva yāgubhattādīhi ca mātaraṃ paṭijaggi. 
503568,112,3801,35,64,1,149,21,"Atha naṃ mātā‘‘ tāta, tava aññānipi gharāvāsakiccāni atthi, ekaṃ samajātikaṃ kulakumārikaṃ gaṇhāhi, sā maṃ posessati, tvampi attano kammaṃ karissasī’’ ti āha."
503569,112,3801,65,83,1,91,12,"‘‘ Amma, ahaṃ attano hitasukhaṃ apaccāsīsamāno tumhe upaṭṭhahāmi, ko añño evaṃ upaṭṭhahissatī’’ ti?"
503570,112,3801,84,95,1,45,6,"‘‘ Kulavaḍḍhanakammaṃ nāma tāta, kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti."
503571,112,3801,96,112,1,86,11,"‘‘ Na mayhaṃ gharāvāsena attho, ahaṃ tumhe upaṭṭhahitvā tumhākaṃ dhūmakāle pabbajissāmī’’ ti. "
503572,112,3801,113,125,1,106,12,Athassa mātā punappunaṃ yācitvāpi manaṃ alabhamānā tassa chandaṃ aggahetvā samajātikaṃ kulakumārikaṃ ānesi. 
503573,112,3801,126,133,1,56,7,So mātaraṃ appaṭikkhipitvā tāya saddhiṃ saṃvāsaṃ kappesi. 
503574,112,3801,134,158,1,144,18,"Sāpi‘‘ mayhaṃ sāmiko mahantena ussāhena mātaraṃ upaṭṭhahati, ahampi naṃ upaṭṭhahissāmi, evamassa piyā bhavissāmī’’ ti cintetvā taṃ sakkaccaṃ upaṭṭhahi. "
503575,112,3801,159,176,1,106,13,So‘‘ ayaṃ me mātaraṃ sakkaccaṃ upaṭṭhahī’’ ti tato paṭṭhāya laddhaladdhāni madhurakhādanīyādīni tassāyeva deti. 
503576,112,3801,177,205,1,188,21,"Sā aparabhāge cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ laddhaladdhāni madhurakhādanīyādīni mayhaññeva deti, addhā mātaraṃ nīharitukāmo bhavissati, nīharaṇūpāyamassā karissāmī’’ ti evaṃ ayoniso ummujjitvā ekaṃ divasaṃ āha–"
503577,112,3801,206,220,1,52,9,"‘‘ sāmi, tayi bahi nikkhamante tava mātā maṃ akkosatī’’ ti. "
503578,112,3801,221,224,1,14,3,So tuṇhī ahosi. 
503579,112,3802,2,4,1,10,2,Sā cintesi–
503580,112,3802,5,16,1,58,7,‘‘ imaṃ mahallikaṃ ujjhāpetvā puttassa paṭikūlaṃ kāressāmī’’ ti. 
503581,112,3802,17,30,1,81,13,Tato paṭṭhāya yāguṃ dadamānā accuṇhaṃ vā atisītalaṃ vā atiloṇaṃ vā aloṇaṃ vā deti.
503582,112,3802,31,51,1,67,11,"‘‘ Amma, accuṇhā’’ ti vā‘‘ atiloṇā’’ ti vā vutte pūretvā sītodakaṃ pakkhipati. "
503583,112,3802,52,92,1,145,22,"Puna‘‘ atisītalā , aloṇāyevā’’ ti vutte‘‘ idāneva‘ accuṇhā, atiloṇā’ ti vatvā puna‘ atisītalā, aloṇā’ ti vadasi, kā taṃ tosetuṃ sakkhissatī’’ ti mahāsaddaṃ karoti. "
503584,112,3802,93,98,1,46,5,Nhānodakampi accuṇhaṃ katvā piṭṭhiyaṃ āsiñcati.
503585,112,3802,99,115,1,67,11,"‘‘ Amma, piṭṭhi me dahatī’’ ti ca vutte puna pūretvā sītodakaṃ pakkhipati."
503586,112,3802,116,150,1,137,20,"‘‘ Atisītaṃ, ammā’’ ti vutte‘‘ idāneva‘ accuṇhan’ ti vatvā puna‘ atisītan’ ti vadati, kā etissā avamānaṃ sahituṃ sakkhissatī’’ ti paṭivissakānaṃ kathesi."
503587,112,3802,151,180,1,131,20,"‘‘ Amma, mañcake me bahū maṅgulā’’ ti ca vuttā mañcakaṃ nīharitvā tassa upari attano mañcakaṃ pothetvā‘‘ pothito me’’ ti atiharitvā paññapeti. "
503588,112,3802,181,199,1,123,13,"Mahāupāsikā diguṇehi maṅgulehi khajjamānā sabbarattiṃ nisinnāva vītināmetvā‘‘ amma, sabbarattiṃ maṅgulehi khāditāmhī’’ ti vadati. "
503589,112,3802,200,277,1,363,54,"Itarā‘‘ hiyyo te mañcako pothito, kā imissā kiccaṃ nittharituṃ sakkotī’’ ti paṭivatvā‘‘ idāni naṃ puttena ujjhāpessāmī’’ ti tattha tattha kheḷasiṅghāṇikādīni vippakiritvā‘‘ kā imaṃ sakalagehaṃ asuciṃ karotī’’ ti vutte‘‘ mātā te evarūpaṃ karoti,‘ mā karī’ ti vuccamānā kalahaṃ karoti, ahaṃ evarūpāya kāḷakaṇṇiyā saddhiṃ ekagehe vasituṃ na sakkomi, etaṃ vā ghare vasāpehi, maṃ vā’’ ti āha. "
503590,112,3803,2,35,1,176,25,"So tassā vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ bhadde, tvaṃ taruṇā yattha katthaci gantvā jīvituṃ sakkā, mātā pana me jarādubbalā, ahamevassā paṭisaraṇaṃ, tvaṃ nikkhamitvā attano kulagehaṃ gacchāhī’’ ti āha. "
503591,112,3803,36,73,1,218,28,"Sā tassa vacanaṃ sutvā bhītā cintesi‘‘ na sakkā imaṃ mātu antare bhindituṃ, ekaṃsenassa mātā piyā, sace panāhaṃ kulagharaṃ gamissaṃ, vidhavavāsaṃ vasantī dukkhitā bhavissāmi, purimanayeneva sassuṃ ārādhetvā paṭijaggissāmī’’ ti . "
503592,112,3803,74,80,1,47,6,Sā tato paṭṭhāya purimasadisameva taṃ paṭijaggi. 
503593,112,3803,81,91,1,97,10,Athekadivasaṃ so uposako dhammassavanatthāya jetavanaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi.
503594,112,3803,92,158,1,313,46,"‘‘ Kiṃ, upāsaka, tvaṃ puññakammesu na pamajjasi, mātuupaṭṭhānakammaṃ pūresī’’ ti ca vutto‘‘ āma, bhante, sā pana mama mātā mayhaṃ aruciyāyeva ekaṃ kuladārikaṃ ānesi, sā idañcidañca anācārakammaṃ akāsī’’ ti sabbaṃ satthu ācikkhitvā‘‘ iti bhagavā sā itthī neva maṃ mātu antare bhindituṃ sakkhi, idāni naṃ sakkaccaṃ upaṭṭhahatī’’ ti āha. "
503595,112,3803,159,195,1,197,30,"Satthā tassa kathaṃ sutvā‘‘ idāni tāva tvaṃ upāsaka, tassā vacanaṃ na akāsi, pubbe panetissā vacanena tava mātaraṃ nikkaḍḍhitvā maṃ nissāya puna gehaṃ ānetvā paṭijaggī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
503596,112,3804,2,22,1,184,19,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente aññatarassa kulassa putto pitari kālakate mātudevato hutvā vuttaniyāmeneva mātaraṃ paṭijaggīti sabbaṃ heṭṭhā kathitanayeneva vitthāretabbaṃ .
503597,112,3804,23,77,1,244,38,"‘‘ Ahaṃ evarūpāya kāḷakaṇṇiyā saddhiṃ vasituṃ na sakkomi, etaṃ vā ghare vasāpehi, maṃ vā’’ ti vutte tassā kathaṃ gahetvā‘‘ mātuyeva me doso’’ ti mātaraṃ āha‘‘ amma, tvaṃ niccaṃ imasmiṃ ghare kalahaṃ karosi, ito nikkhamitvā aññasmiṃ yathārucite ṭhāne vasāhī’’ ti. "
503598,112,3804,78,95,1,97,13,Sā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti rodamānā nikkhamitvā ekaṃ samiddhakulaṃ nissāya bhatiṃ katvā dukkhena jīvikaṃ kappesi. 
503599,112,3804,96,102,1,54,6,Sassuyā gharā nikkhantakāle suṇisāya gabbho patiṭṭhahi. 
503600,112,3804,103,126,1,130,18,"Sā‘‘ tāya kāḷakaṇṇiyā gehe vasamānāya gabbhampi na paṭilabhiṃ, idāni me gabbho laddho’’ ti patino ca paṭivissakānañca kathentī vicarati. "
503601,112,3805,2,29,1,149,21,"Aparabhāge puttaṃ vijāyitvā sāmikaṃ āha‘‘ tava mātari gehe vasamānāya puttaṃ na labhiṃ, idāni me laddho, imināpi kāraṇena tassā kāḷakaṇṇibhāvaṃ jānāhī’’ ti. "
503602,112,3805,30,77,1,239,34,"Itarā‘‘ mama kira nikkaḍḍhitakāle puttaṃ labhī’’ ti sutvā cintesi‘‘ addhā imasmiṃ loke dhammo mato bhavissati, sace hi dhammo mato na bhaveyya, mātaraṃ pothetvā nikkaḍḍhantā puttaṃ na labheyyuṃ, sukhaṃ na jīveyyuṃ, dhammassa matakabhattaṃ dassāmī’’ ti. "
503603,112,3805,78,108,1,261,30,Sā ekadivasaṃ tilapiṭṭhañca taṇḍulañca pacanathāliñca dabbiñca ādāya āmakasusānaṃ gantvā tīhi manussasīsehi uddhanaṃ katvā aggiṃ jāletvā udakaṃ oruyha sasīsaṃ nhatvā sāṭakaṃ nivāsetvā mukhaṃ vikkhāletvā uddhanaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā kese mocetvā taṇḍule dhovituṃ ārabhi. 
