504008,112,4002,17,95,1,344,55,"So āha‘‘ ahaṃ, deva, dakkhiṇadvāre kapaṇitthiyā saddhiṃ saṃvāsaṃ kappesiṃ, sā maṃ‘ chaṇaṃ kīḷissāma, atthi te kiñci hatthe’ ti pucchi, atha naṃ ahaṃ‘ mama nidhānaṃ uttaradvāre pākārantare ṭhapitan’ ti avacaṃ, sā‘ gaccha taṃ āhara, ubhopi kīḷissāmā’ ti maṃ pahiṇi, sā me tassā kathā hadayaṃ na vijahati, taṃ maṃ anussarantaṃ kāmatapo tapati, ayaṃ me, deva, attho’’ ti. "
