504226,112,4108,133,164,1,184,23,"Tatiyaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ tvaṃ, tāta, pacchimadvārena nikkhamitvā ujukameva gacchanto kesarasīhaṃ passissasi, tāya saññāya tattha nagaraṃ māpetvā vasa, taṃ nagaraṃ sīhapuraṃ nāma bhavissatī’’ ti āha. "
504227,112,4108,165,198,1,208,24,"Catutthaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ tvaṃ, tāta, uttaradvārena nikkhamitvā ujukameva gacchanto sabbaratanamayaṃ cakkapañjaraṃ passissasi, tāya saññāya tattha nagaraṃ māpetvā vasa, taṃ nagaraṃ uttarapañcālaṃ nāma bhavissatī’’ ti āha. "
504228,112,4108,199,246,1,311,39,"Pañcamaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ tāta, tayā imasmiṃ ṭhāne vasituṃ na sakkā, imasmiṃ nagare mahāthūpaṃ katvā nikkhamitvā pacchimuttarāya disāya ujukameva gacchanto dve pabbate aññamaññaṃ paharitvā paharitvā daddarasaddaṃ karonte passissasi, tāya saññāya tattha nagaraṃ māpetvā vasa, taṃ nagaraṃ daddarapuraṃ nāma bhavissatī’’ ti āha. "
504229,112,4108,247,260,1,85,13,Te pañcapi janā tāya tāya saññāya gantvā tasmiṃ tasmiṃ ṭhāne nagarāni māpetvā vasiṃsu. 
504230,112,4109,2,27,1,136,17,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepi devadatto musāvādaṃ katvā pathaviṃ paviṭṭho’’ ti vatvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
504231,112,4109,28,42,1,69,9,"‘‘ tadā cetiyarājā devadatto ahosi, kapilabrāhmaṇo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
504232,112,4110,2,4,1,27,2,Cetiyajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
504233,112,4112,2,7,1,20,2,[ 423]7. Indriyajātakavaṇṇanā 
504234,112,4113,2,13,1,88,10,Yo indriyānan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto purāṇadutiyikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
504235,112,4113,14,46,1,273,27,"Sāvatthiyaṃ kireko kulaputto satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā‘‘ na sakkā agāramajjhe vasantena ekantaparipuṇṇaṃ ekantaparisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carituṃ, niyyānikasāsane pabbajitvā dukkhassantaṃ karissāmī’’ ti ghare vibhavaṃ puttadārassa niyyādetvā nikkhamitvā satthāraṃ pabbajjaṃ yāci. "
504236,112,4113,47,50,1,28,3,Satthāpissa pabbajjaṃ dāpesi. 
504237,112,4113,51,76,1,191,24,"Tassa ācariyupajjhāyehi saddhiṃ piṇḍāya carato navakattā ceva bhikkhūnaṃ bahubhāvena ca kulaghare vā āsanasālāya vā āsanaṃ na pāpuṇāti, saṅghanavakānaṃ koṭiyaṃ pīṭhakaṃ vā phalakaṃ vā pāpuṇāti. "
504238,112,4113,77,91,1,126,13,"Āhāropi uḷuṅkapiṭṭhena ghaṭṭitā bhinnasitthakayāgu vā pūtisukkhakhajjakaṃ vā jhāmasukkhakūro vā pāpuṇāti, yāpanapamāṇaṃ na hoti. "
504239,112,4113,92,100,1,60,7,So attanā laddhaṃ gahetvā purāṇadutiyikāya santikaṃ gacchati. 
504240,112,4113,101,112,1,104,11,Athassa sā pattaṃ gahetvā vanditvā pattato bhattaṃ nīharitvā susampāditāni yāgubhattasūpabyañjanāni deti. 
504241,112,4113,113,120,1,66,7,Mahallako rasataṇhāya bajjhitvā purāṇadutiyikaṃ jahituṃ na sakkoti. 
504242,112,4113,121,135,1,49,9,"Sā cintesi‘‘ baddho nu kho, noti vīmaṃsissāmi nan’’ ti. "
504243,112,4114,2,15,1,146,13,Athekadivasaṃ janapadamanussaṃ setamattikāya nhāpetvā gehe nisīdāpetvā aññepissa katipaye parivāramanusse āṇāpetvā thokathokaṃ pānabhojanaṃ dāpesi. 
504244,112,4114,16,20,1,31,4,Te khādantā bhuñjantā nisīdiṃsu. 
504245,112,4114,21,36,1,106,14,"Gehadvāre ca cakkesu goṇe bandhāpetvā ekaṃ sakaṭampi ṭhapāpesi, sayaṃ pana piṭṭhigabbhe nisīditvā pūve paci. "
504246,112,4114,37,41,1,31,4,Mahallako āgantvā dvāre aṭṭhāsi. 
504247,112,4114,42,58,1,63,11,"Taṃ disvā eko mahallakapuriso‘‘ ayye, eko thero dvāre ṭhito’’ ti āha."
504248,112,4114,59,66,1,23,3,‘‘ Vanditvā aticchāpehī’’ ti. 
504249,112,4114,67,92,1,97,15,"So‘‘ aticchatha, bhante’’ ti punappunaṃ kathetvāpi taṃ agacchantaṃ disvā‘‘ ayye, thero na gacchatī’’ ti āha. "
504250,112,4114,93,163,1,385,53,"Sā āgantvā sāṇiṃ ukkhipitvā oloketvā‘‘ ambho ayaṃ mama dārakapitā’’ ti vatvā nikkhamitvā pattaṃ gahetvā gehaṃ pavesetvā parivisitvā bhojanapariyosāne vanditvā‘‘ bhante, tumhe idheva parinibbāyatha, mayaṃ ettakaṃ kālaṃ aññaṃ kulaṃ na gaṇhimha, asāmike pana ghare gharāvāso na saṇṭhāti, mayaṃ aññaṃ kulaṃ gaṇhāma, dūraṃ janapadaṃ gacchissāma, tumhe appamattā hotha, sace me doso atthi, khamathā’’ ti āha. "
504251,112,4114,164,168,1,41,4,Mahallakassa hadayaphālanakālo viya ahosi. 
504252,112,4114,169,197,1,137,19,"Atha naṃ‘‘ ahaṃ taṃ jahituṃ na sakkomi, mā gaccha, vibbhamissāmi, asukaṭṭhāne me sāṭakaṃ pesehi, pattacīvaraṃ paṭicchāpetvā āgacchissāmī’’ ti āha. "
504253,112,4114,198,206,1,23,4,Sā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
504254,112,4114,207,236,1,156,19,"Mahallako vihāraṃ gantvā ācariyupajjhāye pattacīvaraṃ paṭicchāpento‘‘ kasmā, āvuso, evaṃ karosī’’ ti vutto‘‘ purāṇadutiyikaṃ jahituṃ na sakkomi vibbhamissāmī’’ ti āha. "
504255,112,4114,237,268,1,153,20,"Atha naṃ te anicchantaññeva satthu santikaṃ netvā‘‘ kiṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ anicchantaññeva ānayitthā’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhante, ayaṃ ukkaṇṭhitvā vibbhamitukāmo’’ ti vadiṃsu. "
504256,112,4114,269,283,1,63,10,Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchi.
504257,112,4114,284,292,1,16,3,"‘‘ Saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti."
504258,112,4114,293,301,1,22,4,‘‘ Ko taṃ ukkaṇṭhāpesī’’ ti?
504259,112,4114,302,342,1,226,31,"‘‘ Purāṇadutiyikā bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhu na idāneva sā itthī tuyhaṃ anatthakārikā, pubbepi tvaṃ taṃ nissāya catūhi jhānehi parihīno mahādukkhaṃ patvā maṃ nissāya tamhā dukkhā muccitvā naṭṭhajjhānaṃ paṭilabhī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
