504262,112,4115,33,55,1,227,22,So vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā rañño sippaṃ dassetvā issariyaṃ pahāya kañci ajānāpetvā aggadvārena nikkhamitvā araññaṃ pavisitvā sakkadattiye kaviṭṭhakaassame isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā jhānābhiññāyo nibbattesi. 
