504448,112,4198,60,70,1,71,9,Appampi {ce}ti thokampi ce deyyadhammaṃ kammañca phalañca saddahanto deti. 
504449,112,4198,71,84,1,100,11,"Teneva {so}ti tena parittadeyyadhammavatthukena parittakenāpi cāgena so parattha sukhī hoti, mahārājāti. "
504450,112,4199,2,9,1,64,7,Viceyya dānan ti dakkhiṇañca dakkhiṇeyyañca vicinitvā dinnadānaṃ. 
504451,112,4199,10,36,1,188,25,"Tattha yaṃ vā taṃ vā adatvā aggaṃ paṇītaṃ deyyadhammaṃ vicinitvā dadanto dakkhiṇaṃ vicināti nāma, yesaṃ tesaṃ vā adatvā sīlādiguṇasampanne vicinitvā tesaṃ dadanto dakkhiṇeyyaṃ vicināti nāma. "
504452,112,4199,37,43,1,53,6,Sugatappasatthan ti evarūpaṃ dānaṃ buddhehi pasatthaṃ. 
504453,112,4199,44,55,1,65,7,Tattha dakkhiṇeyyavicinanaṃ dassetuṃ‘‘ ye dakkhiṇeyyā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
504454,112,4199,56,62,1,54,5,Tattha {dakkhiṇeyyā}ti dakkhiṇāya anucchavikā buddhādayo. 
504455,112,4200,2,6,1,36,3,{Pāṇabhūtānī}ti pāṇasaṅkhātāni bhūtāni. 
504456,112,4200,7,13,1,51,6,Aheṭhayaṃ caran ti kāruññena aviheṭhayanto caramāno. 
