504458,112,4200,21,24,1,25,3,Bhīrun ti upavādabhīrukaṃ. 
504459,112,4200,25,40,1,97,14,"Na tattha sūran ti yo pana ayonisomanasikārena tasmiṃ upavāde sūro hoti, taṃ paṇḍitā nappasaṃsanti. "
504460,112,4200,41,50,1,53,8,Bhayā {hī}ti upavādabhayena hi paṇḍitā pāpaṃ na karonti. 
504461,112,4201,2,16,1,126,11,"Hīnena {brahmacariyenā}ti bāhiratitthāyatane tāva methunaviratisīlamattakaṃ hīnaṃ brahmacariyaṃ nāma, tena khattiyakule uppajjati. "
504462,112,4201,17,24,1,56,6,"Jhānassa upacāramattaṃ majjhimaṃ, tena devaloke uppajjati. "
504463,112,4201,25,35,1,68,8,"Aṭṭha samāpattiyo uttamaṃ, tena brahmaloke uppajjanto visujjhati nāma. "
504464,112,4201,36,59,1,205,20,"Sāsane pana sīlavantasseva ekaṃ devanikāyaṃ paṇidhāya brahmacariyaṃ hīnaṃ nāma, parisuddhasīlasseva samāpattinibbattanaṃ majjhimaṃ nāma, parisuddhasīle ṭhatvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattuppatti uttamaṃ nāma. "
504465,112,4202,2,21,1,188,16,"Osānagāthāya ayamattho– mahārāja, kiñcāpi ekaṃseneva dānaṃ bahudhā pasatthaṃ vaṇṇitaṃ, dānato pana samathavipassanāsaṅkhātaṃ nibbānasaṅkhātañca dhammakoṭṭhāsabhūtaṃ dhammapadameva uttaritaraṃ. "
504466,112,4202,22,23,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
504467,112,4202,24,39,1,162,15,Pubbeva hi imasmiṃ kappe kassapadasabalādayo pubbatareva vessabhūdasabalādayo santo sappurisā sapaññā samathavipassanaṃ bhāvetvā nibbānameva ajjhagamuṃ adhigatāti. 
504468,112,4203,2,16,1,140,14,Evaṃ satta paccekabuddhā anumodanāya rañño amatamahānibbānaṃ vaṇṇetvā rājānaṃ appamādena ovaditvā vuttanayeneva attano vasanaṭṭhānameva gatā. 
504469,112,4203,17,28,1,87,11,Rājāpi saddhiṃ aggamahesiyā dānaṃ datvā yāvajīvaṃ ṭhatvā tato cavitvā saggapuraṃ pūresi. 
504470,112,4204,2,20,1,105,14,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā‘‘ evaṃ pubbepi paṇḍitā viceyya dānaṃ adaṃsū’’ ti vatvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
504471,112,4204,21,38,1,102,11,"‘‘ tadā paccekabuddhā parinibbāyiṃsu, samuddavijayā rāhulamātā ahosi, roruvamahārājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
504472,112,4205,2,4,1,27,2,Ādittajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
504473,112,4207,2,7,1,20,2,[ 425]9. Aṭṭhānajātakavaṇṇanā 
504474,112,4208,2,13,1,87,10,Gaṅgā {kumudinī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
504475,112,4208,14,59,1,192,26,"Tañhi bhikkhuṃ satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ kiṃkāraṇā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kilesavasenā’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhu mātugāmo nāma akataññū mittadubbhī avissāsanīyo. "
504476,112,4208,60,68,1,70,8,Atīte paṇḍitā devasikaṃ sahassaṃ dentāpi mātugāmaṃ tosetuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu. 
504477,112,4208,69,95,1,151,20,"Sā ekadivasamattaṃ sahassaṃ alabhitvāva te gīvāyaṃ gāhāpetvā nīharāpesi , evaṃ akataññū mātugāmo, mā tassa kāraṇā kilesavasaṃ gacchā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
504478,112,4209,2,18,1,124,14,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente tassa ca putto brahmadattakumāro, bārāṇasiseṭṭhino ca putto mahādhanakumāro nāma. "
504479,112,4209,19,28,1,75,8,"Te ubhopi sahapaṃsukīḷakā sahāyakā ahesuṃ, ekācariyakuleyeva sippaṃ gaṇhiṃsu. "
504480,112,4209,29,38,1,76,8,"Rājakumāro pitu accayena rajje patiṭṭhāsi, seṭṭhiputtopissa santikeyeva ahosi. "
504481,112,4209,39,46,1,71,7,Bārāṇasiyañca ekā nagarasobhiṇī vaṇṇadāsī abhirūpā ahosi sobhaggappattā. 
504482,112,4209,47,68,1,168,20,"Seṭṭhiputto devasikaṃ sahassaṃ datvā niccakāle tāyeva saddhiṃ abhiramanto pitu accayena seṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ labhitvāpi na taṃ vijahi, tatheva devasikaṃ sahassaṃ datvā abhirami. "
504483,112,4209,69,75,1,54,6,Seṭṭhiputto divasassa tayo vāre rājupaṭṭhānaṃ gacchati. 
504484,112,4209,76,88,1,107,11,"Athassa ekadivasaṃ rājupaṭṭhānaṃ gatassa raññā saddhiṃ samullapantasseva sūriyo atthaṅgami, andhakāraṃ jātaṃ. "
504485,112,4209,89,112,1,147,18,"So rājakulā nikkhamitvā‘‘ idāni gehaṃ gantvā āgamanavelā natthi, nagarasobhiṇiyāyeva gehaṃ gamissāmī’’ ti upaṭṭhāke uyyojetvā ekakova tassā gehaṃ pāvisi. "
504486,112,4209,113,127,1,51,9,"Atha naṃ sā disvā‘‘ ayyaputta, sahassaṃ ābhatan’’ ti āha."
504487,112,4209,128,154,1,128,19,"‘‘ Bhadde, ahaṃ ajjeva ativikālo jāto, tasmā gehaṃ agantvā manusse uyyojetvā ekakova paviṭṭhosmi, sve pana te dve sahassāni dassāmī’’ ti. "
504488,112,4210,2,28,1,146,19,"Sā cintesi‘‘ sacāhaṃ ajja okāsaṃ karissāmi, aññesupi divasesu tucchahatthakova āgamissati, evaṃ me dhanaṃ parihāyissati, na dānissa okāsaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
504489,112,4210,29,49,1,88,14,"Atha naṃ evamāha‘‘ sāmi, mayaṃ vaṇṇadāsiyo nāma, amhākaṃ sahassaṃ adatvā keḷi nāma natthī’’ ti."
504490,112,4210,50,63,1,48,7,"‘‘ Bhadde, sve diguṇaṃ āharissāmī’’ ti punappunaṃ yāci. "
504491,112,4210,64,86,1,121,17,"Nagarasobhiṇī dāsiyo āṇāpesi‘‘ etassa idha ṭhatvā maṃ oloketuṃ mā adattha, gīvāyaṃ taṃ gahetvā nīharitvā dvāraṃ pidahathā’’ ti. "
504492,112,4210,87,92,1,30,5,Taṃ sutvā dāsiyo tathā kariṃsu. 
504493,112,4210,93,123,1,178,24,"Atha so cintesi‘‘ ahaṃ imāya saddhiṃ asītikoṭidhanaṃ khādiṃ, sā maṃ ekadivasaṃ tucchahatthaṃ disvā gīvāyaṃ gahetvā nīharāpesi, aho mātugāmo nāma pāpo nillajjo akataññū mittadubbhī’’ ti. "
504494,112,4210,124,168,1,333,36,"So mātugāmassa aguṇaṃ anussarantova virajji, paṭikūlasaññaṃ paṭilabhi, gharāvāsepi ukkaṇṭhito ‘‘ kiṃ me gharāvāsena, ajjeva nikkhamitvā pabbajissāmī’’ ti puna gehaṃ agantvā rājānampi adisvāva nagarā nikkhamitvā araññaṃ pavisitvā gaṅgātīre assamaṃ māpetvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā jhānābhiññāyo uppādetvā vanamūlaphalāhāro tattha vāsaṃ kappesi. "
504495,112,4211,2,14,1,46,8,Rājā taṃ apassanto‘‘ kahaṃ mama sahāyo’’ ti pucchi. 
504496,112,4211,15,20,1,55,5,Nagarasobhiṇiyāpi katakammaṃ sakalanagare pākaṭaṃ jātaṃ. 
504497,112,4211,21,42,1,121,16,"Athassa tamatthaṃ ācikkhitvā‘‘ iti te deva, sahāyo lajjāya gharampi agantvā araññaṃ pavisitvā pabbajito bhavissatī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
504498,112,4211,43,66,1,141,18,Rājā taṃ sutvā nagarasobhiṇiṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ ekadivasaṃ sahassaṃ alabhitvā mama sahāyaṃ gīvāyaṃ gāhāpetvā nīharāpesī’’ ti pucchi.
504499,112,4211,67,75,1,14,3,"‘‘ Saccaṃ, devā’’ ti."
504500,112,4211,76,99,1,97,16,"‘‘ Pāpe jammī, sīghaṃ mama sahāyassa gataṭṭhānaṃ gantvā taṃ ānehi, no ce ānessasi, jīvitaṃ te natthī’’ ti. "
504501,112,4211,100,182,1,426,61,"Sā rañño vacanaṃ sutvā bhītā rathaṃ āruyha mahantena parivārena nagarā nikkhamitvā tassa vasanaṭṭhānaṃ pariyesantī sutavasena taṃ ṭhānaṃ sutvā tattha gantvā vanditvā‘‘ ayya, mayā andhabālabhāvena kataṃ dosaṃ khamatha, ahaṃ na punevaṃ karissāmī’’ ti yācitvā‘‘ sādhu, khamāmi te, natthi me tayi āghāto’’ ti vutte‘‘ sace me khamatha, mayā saddhiṃ rathaṃ abhiruhatha, nagaraṃ gacchissāma, gatakāle yaṃ mama ghare dhanaṃ atthi, sabbaṃ dassāmī’’ ti āha. "
504502,112,4211,183,219,1,175,28,"So tassā vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ bhadde, idāni tayā saddhiṃ gantuṃ na sakkā, yadā pana imasmiṃ loke yena na bhavitabbaṃ, taṃ bhavissati, api nāma tadā gaccheyyan’’ ti vatvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
504503,112,4212,2,4,1,0,0,77.
504504,112,4213,2,11,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Gaṅgā kumudinī santā, saṅkhavaṇṇā ca kokilā; "
504505,112,4214,2,13,1,45,8,"Jambū tālaphalaṃ dajjā, atha nūna tadā siyā’’ ti. "
504506,112,4215,2,35,1,222,28,"Tassattho – bhadde, yathā hi kumudasarā kumudehi sañchannā tiṭṭhanti, tatheva sace sakalāpi mahāgaṅgā kumudinī sīghasotaṃ pahāya santā upasantā siyā, sabbe kokilā ca saṅkhavaṇṇā bhaveyyuṃ, sabbo jamburukkho ca tālaphalaṃ dadeyya. "
504507,112,4215,36,53,1,95,15,"Atha nūna tadā {siyā}ti atha tādise kāle amhākampi samāgamo nūna siyā, bhaveyya nāmāti vuttaṃ hoti. "
