504942,112,4472,14,25,1,124,11,Tañhi bhikkhuṃ ekaṃ alaṅkatamātugāmaṃ disvā ukkaṇṭhitaṃ dīghakesanakhalomaṃ vibbhamitukāmaṃ ācariyupajjhāyehi aruciyā ānītaṃ. 
504943,112,4472,26,83,1,263,35,"Satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ kiṃkāraṇā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ alaṅkatamātugāmaṃ disvā kilesavasena, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhu kileso nāma guṇaviddhaṃsako appassādo niraye nibbattāpeti, esa pana kileso kiṃkāraṇā taṃ na kilamessati? "
