505236,112,4591,2,7,1,26,2,[ 433]7. Lomasakassapajātakavaṇṇanā 
505237,112,4592,2,14,1,91,11,Assa indasamo {rājā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
505238,112,4592,15,67,1,293,36,"Tañhi bhikkhuṃ satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccan’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhu sinerukampanavāto kiṃ purāṇapaṇṇāni na kampessati, yasasamaṅginopi sappurisā āyasakyaṃ pāpuṇanti, kilesā nāmete parisuddhasattepi saṃkiliṭṭhe karonti, pageva tādisan’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
505239,112,4593,2,23,1,175,19,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente brahmadattassa putto brahmadattakumāro nāma purohitaputto ca kassapo nāma dve sahāyakā hutvā ekācariyakule sabbasippāni uggaṇhiṃsu. 
505240,112,4593,24,30,1,59,6,Aparabhāge brahmadattakumāro pitu accayena rajje patiṭṭhāsi. 
505241,112,4593,31,59,1,149,21,"Kassapo cintesi‘‘ mayhaṃ sahāyo rājā jāto, idāni me mahantaṃ issariyaṃ dassati, kiṃ me issariyena, ahaṃ mātāpitaro ca rājānañca āpucchitvā pabbajissāmī’’ ti. "
505242,112,4593,60,79,1,164,19,So rājānañca mātāpitaro ca āpucchitvā himavantaṃ pavisitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā sattame divase abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā uñchācariyāya yāpento vihāsi. 
