505283,112,4612,48,56,1,27,4,‘‘ Mayā pesitopi nāgacchatī’’ ti.
505284,112,4612,57,98,1,224,30,"‘‘ Tena hi, mahārāja, attano dhītaraṃ candavatiṃ kumārikaṃ alaṅkaritvā seyyaṃ tatheva pesetvā‘ sace kira āgantvā yaññaṃ yajissasi, rājā te imaṃ kumārikaṃ dassatī’ ti vadāpehi, addhā so kumārikāya paṭibaddhacitto hutvā āgacchissatī’’ ti. "
505285,112,4612,99,112,1,70,9,Rājā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā punadivase seyyassa hatthe dhītaraṃ adāsi. 
505286,112,4612,113,128,1,138,15,So rājadhītaraṃ gahetvā tattha gantvā isiṃ vanditvā paṭisanthāraṃ katvā devaccharapaṭibhāgaṃ rājadhītaraṃ tassa dassetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. 
505287,112,4612,129,142,1,94,12,"Atha isi indriyāni bhinditvā taṃ olokesi, saha olokaneneva paṭibaddhacitto hutvā jhānā parihāyi. "
505288,112,4612,143,167,1,133,18,"Amacco tassa paṭibaddhacittabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ bhante, sace kira yaññaṃ yajissatha, rājā te imaṃ dārikaṃ pādaparicārikaṃ katvā dassatī’’ ti āha. "
505289,112,4612,168,181,1,52,9,So kilesavasena kampanto‘‘ imaṃ kira me dassatī’’ ti āha.
505290,112,4612,182,193,1,35,6,"‘‘ Āma, yaññaṃ yajantassa te dassatī’’ ti. "
505291,112,4612,194,213,1,110,15,So‘‘ sādhu imaṃ labhanto yajissāmī’’ ti vatvā taṃ gahetvā saheva jaṭāhi alaṅkatarathaṃ abhiruyha bārāṇasiṃ agamāsi. 
