505485,112,4720,2,15,1,86,10,Kuto nu {āgacchathā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
505486,112,4720,16,70,1,306,38,"Tañhi satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ kasmā bhikkhu mātugāmaṃ patthesi, mātugāmo nāmesa asabbho akataññū, pubbe dānavarakkhasā gilitvā kucchinā pariharantāpi mātugāmaṃ rakkhituṃ ekapurisanissitaṃ kātuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu, tvaṃ kathaṃ sakkhissasī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
505487,112,4721,2,22,1,178,20,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāme pahāya himavantaṃ pavisitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā phalāphalena yāpento vihāsi. 
505488,112,4721,23,29,1,51,6,Tassa paṇṇasālāya avidūre eko dānavarakkhaso vasati. 
505489,112,4721,30,46,1,135,15,"So antarantarā mahāsattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā dhammaṃ suṇāti, aṭaviyaṃ pana manussānaṃ sañcaraṇamagge ṭhatvā āgatāgate manusse gahetvā khādati. "
505490,112,4721,47,57,1,92,10,Tasmiṃ kāle ekā kāsiraṭṭhe kuladhītā uttamarūpadharā aññatarasmiṃ paccantagāme nivutthā hoti. 
505491,112,4721,58,70,1,121,12,Tassā ekadivasaṃ mātāpitūnaṃ dassanatthāya gantvā paccāgamanakāle parivāramanusse disvā so dānavo bheravarūpena pakkhandi. 
505492,112,4721,71,76,1,53,5,Manussā bhītā gahitagahitāvudhāni chaḍḍetvā palāyiṃsu. 
505493,112,4721,77,91,1,106,14,Dānavo yāne nisinnaṃ abhirūpaṃ mātugāmaṃ disvā paṭibaddhacitto hutvā taṃ attano guhaṃ netvā bhariyaṃ akāsi. 
505494,112,4721,92,115,1,212,21,"Tato paṭṭhāya sappitelataṇḍulamacchamaṃsādīni ceva madhuraphalāphalāni ca āharitvā taṃ posesi, vatthālaṅkārehi ca naṃ alaṅkaritvā rakkhaṇatthāya ekasmiṃ karaṇḍake pakkhipitvā karaṇḍakaṃ gilitvā kucchinā pariharati. "
505495,112,4721,116,153,1,257,32,So ekadivasaṃ nhāyitukāmatāya ekaṃ saraṃ gantvā karaṇḍakaṃ uggilitvā taṃ tato nīharitvā nhāpetvā vilimpetvā alaṅkāretvā‘‘ thokaṃ tava sarīraṃ utuṃ gaṇhāpehī’’ ti taṃ karaṇḍakasamīpe ṭhapetvā sayaṃ nhānatitthaṃ otaritvā taṃ anāsaṅkamāno thokaṃ dūraṃ gantvā nhāyi. 
