505649,112,4809,2,32,1,182,24,"Tassattho – āḷi, tava gehe bahubhaṇḍakaṃ atthi, taṃ te nikkhantāya agārasmā anārakkhaṃ bhaṇḍakaṃ vinassati, ahameva te āḷino sahāyakassa ārogyaṃ vajjaṃ vadissāmi, tvaṃ idheva vasa māgamāti. "
505650,112,4810,2,13,1,86,11,Evañca pana vatvā maraṇabhayabhītā vegena sāmikassa santikaṃ gantvā taṃ gahetvā palāyi. 
505651,112,4810,14,20,1,38,6,Te puna taṃ ṭhānaṃ āgantuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu. 
505652,112,4811,2,20,1,121,14,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi‘‘ tadā ahaṃ tasmiṃ ṭhāne vanajeṭṭhakarukkhe nibbattadevatā ahosin’’ ti. 
505653,112,4812,2,4,1,32,2,Pūtimaṃsajātakavaṇṇanā ekādasamā.
505654,112,4814,2,7,1,20,2,[ 438]12. Daddarajātakavaṇṇanā 
505655,112,4815,2,16,1,98,12,Yo te {puttake}ti idaṃ satthā gijjhakūṭe viharanto devadattassa vadhāya parisakkanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
505656,112,4815,17,43,1,241,22,Tasmiñhi samaye dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ aho āvuso devadatto nillajjo anariyo evaṃ uttamaguṇadharassa sammāsambuddhassa ajātasattunā saddhiṃ ekato hutvā dhanuggahapayojanasilāpavijjhananāḷāgirivissajjanehi vadhāya upāyaṃ karotī’’ ti. 
505657,112,4815,44,95,1,224,32,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepi devadatto mayhaṃ vadhāya parisakki, idāni pana me tāsamattampi kātuṃ nāsakkhī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
505658,112,4816,2,38,1,267,30,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente eko disāpāmokkho ācariyo pañcasatānaṃ māṇavakānaṃ sippaṃ vācento ekadivasaṃ cintesi‘‘ mayhaṃ idha vasantassa palibodho hoti, māṇavakānampi sippaṃ na niṭṭhāti, himavantapadese araññāyatanaṃ pavisitvā tattha vasanto vācessāmī’’ ti. "
505659,112,4816,39,58,1,169,18,"So māṇavakānaṃ kathetvā tilataṇḍulatelavatthādīni gāhāpetvā araññaṃ pavisitvā maggato avidūre ṭhāne paṇṇasālaṃ kāretvā nivāsaṃ kappesi, māṇavāpi attano paṇṇasālaṃ kariṃsu. "
505660,112,4816,59,63,1,42,4,Māṇavakānaṃ ñātakā telataṇḍulādīni pesenti. 
505661,112,4816,64,93,1,207,22,"Raṭṭhavāsinopi‘‘ disāpāmokkho ācariyo kira araññe asukaṭṭhāne nāma vasanto sippaṃ uggaṇhāpetī’’ ti tassa taṇḍulādīni abhiharanti, kantārappaṭipannāpi denti, aññataropi puriso khīrapānatthāya savacchaṃ dhenuṃ adāsi. "
505662,112,4816,94,107,1,109,12,"Ācariyassa paṇṇasālāya santike dvīhi potakehi saddhiṃ ekā godhā vasati, sīhabyagghāpissa upaṭṭhānaṃ āgacchanti. "
