506680,113,426,2,7,1,27,2,[ 447]9. Mahādhammapālajātakavaṇṇanā 
506681,113,427,2,20,1,133,17,Kiṃ te vatan ti idaṃ satthā paṭhamagamanena kapilapuraṃ gantvā nigrodhārāme viharanto pitu nivesane rañño asaddahanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
506682,113,427,21,58,1,272,30,"Tadā hi suddhodanamahārājā vīsatisahassabhikkhuparivārassa bhagavato attano nivesane yāgukhajjakaṃ datvā antarābhatte sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ kathento‘‘ bhante, tumhākaṃ padhānakāle devatā āgantvā ākāse ṭhatvā‘ putto te siddhatthakumāro appāhāratāya mato’ ti mayhaṃ ārocesun’’ ti āha. "
506683,113,427,59,98,1,179,25,"Satthārā ca‘‘ saddahi, mahārājā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na saddahiṃ, bhante, ākāse ṭhatvā kathentiyopi devatā,‘ mama puttassa bodhitale buddhattaṃ appatvā parinibbānaṃ nāma natthī’ ti paṭikkhipin’’ ti āha."
506684,113,427,99,141,1,245,32,"‘‘ Mahārāja, pubbepi tvaṃ mahādhammapālakālepi‘ putto te mato imānissa aṭṭhīnī’ ti dassetvā vadantassapi disāpāmokkhācariyassa‘ amhākaṃ kule taruṇakāle kālakiriyā nāma natthī’ ti na saddahi, idāni pana kasmā saddahissasī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
506685,113,428,2,12,1,81,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente kāsiraṭṭhe dhammapālagāmo nāma ahosi. 
506686,113,428,13,19,1,48,6,So dhammapālakulassa vasanatāya etaṃ nāmaṃ labhi. 
506687,113,428,20,46,1,176,19,"Tattha dasannaṃ kusalakammapathānaṃ pālanato‘‘ dhammapālo’’ tveva paññāto brāhmaṇo paṭivasati, tassa kule antamaso dāsakammakarāpi dānaṃ denti, sīlaṃ rakkhanti, uposathakammaṃ karonti. "
506688,113,428,47,61,1,76,9,"Tadā bodhisatto tasmiṃ kule nibbatti,‘‘ dhammapālakumāro’’ tvevassa nāmaṃ kariṃsu. "
506689,113,428,62,71,1,77,9,Atha naṃ vayappattaṃ pitā sahassaṃ datvā sippuggahaṇatthāya takkasilaṃ pesesi. 
506690,113,428,72,84,1,109,11,"So tattha gantvā disāpāmokkhācariyassa santike sippaṃ uggaṇhi, pañcannaṃ māṇavakasatānaṃ jeṭṭhantevāsiko ahosi. "
506691,113,428,85,89,1,38,4,Tadā ācariyassa jeṭṭhaputto kālamakāsi. 
506692,113,428,90,101,1,93,10,Ācariyo māṇavakaparivuto ñātigaṇena saddhiṃ rodanto kandanto susāne tassa sarīrakiccaṃ kāreti. 
506693,113,428,102,117,1,108,14,"Tattha ācariyo ca ñātivaggo cassa antevāsikā ca rodanti paridevanti, dhammapāloyeveko na rodati na paridevati. "
506694,113,428,118,168,1,293,37,"Apica kho pana tesu pañcasatesu māṇavesu susānā āgamma ācariyassa santike nisīditvā‘‘ aho evarūpo nāma ācārasampanno taruṇamāṇavo taruṇakāleyeva mātāpitūhi vippayutto maraṇappatto’’ ti vadantesu‘‘ sammā, tumhe‘ taruṇo’ ti bhaṇatha, atha kasmā taruṇakāleyeva marati, nanu ayuttaṃ taruṇakāle maritun’’ ti āha. "
506695,113,429,2,21,1,80,14,"Atha naṃ te āhaṃsu‘‘ kiṃ pana samma, tvaṃ imesaṃ sattānaṃ maraṇabhāvaṃ na jānāsī’’ ti? "
506696,113,429,22,31,1,61,7,"Jānāmi, taruṇakāle pana na maranti, mahallakakāleyeva marantīti. "
506697,113,429,32,39,1,43,6,Nanu aniccā sabbe saṅkhārā hutvā abhāvinoti?
506698,113,429,40,59,1,91,12,"‘‘ Saccaṃ aniccā, daharakāle pana sattā na maranti, mahallakakāle maranti, aniccataṃ pāpuṇantī’’ ti."
506699,113,429,60,75,1,53,9,"‘‘ Kiṃ samma, dhammapāla, tumhākaṃ gehe na keci marantī’’ ti?"
506700,113,429,76,88,1,55,7,"‘‘ Daharakāle pana na maranti, mahallakakāleyeva marantī’’ ti."
506701,113,429,89,98,1,33,5,‘‘ Kiṃ panesā tumhākaṃ kulapaveṇī’’ ti?
506702,113,429,99,106,1,17,3,‘‘ Āma kulapaveṇī’’ ti. 
506703,113,429,107,113,1,43,6,Māṇavā taṃ tassa kathaṃ ācariyassa ārocesuṃ. 
506704,113,429,114,134,1,98,15,"Atha naṃ so pakkosāpetvā pucchi‘‘ saccaṃ kira tāta dhammapāla, tumhākaṃ kule daharakāle na mīyantī’’ ti?"
506705,113,429,135,142,1,17,3,‘‘ Saccaṃ ācariyā’’ ti. 
506706,113,429,143,172,1,151,22,"So tassa vacanaṃ sutvā cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ ativiya acchariyaṃ vadati, imassa pitu santikaṃ gantvā pucchitvā sace etaṃ saccaṃ, ahampi tameva dhammaṃ pūressāmī’’ ti. "
506707,113,429,173,227,1,358,43,"So puttassa kattabbakiccaṃ katvā sattaṭṭhadivasaccayena dhammapālaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ tāta, ahaṃ khippaṃ āgamissāmi, yāva mamāgamanā ime māṇave sippaṃ vācehī’’ ti vatvā ekassa eḷakassa aṭṭhīni gahetvā dhovitvā pasibbake katvā ekaṃ cūḷupaṭṭhākaṃ ādāya takkasilato nikkhamitvā anupubbena taṃ gāmaṃ patvā‘‘ kataraṃ mahādhammapālassa gehan’’ ti pucchitvā gantvā dvāre aṭṭhāsi. "
506708,113,429,228,249,1,143,18,"Brāhmaṇassa dāsamanussesu yo yo paṭhamaṃ addasa, so so ācariyassa hatthato chattaṃ gaṇhi, upāhanaṃ gaṇhi, upaṭṭhākassapi hatthato pasibbakaṃ gaṇhi."
506709,113,429,250,274,1,116,16,‘‘ Puttassa vo dhammapālakumārassa ācariyo dvāre ṭhitoti kumārassa pitu ārocethā’’ ti ca vuttā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti gantvā ārocayiṃsu. 
506710,113,429,275,294,1,114,15,So vegena dvāramūlaṃ gantvā‘‘ ito ethā’’ ti taṃ gharaṃ abhinetvā pallaṅke nisīdāpetvā sabbaṃ pādadhovanādikiccaṃ akāsi. 
506711,113,430,2,38,1,237,28,"Ācariyo bhuttabhojano sukhakathāya nisinnakāle‘‘ brāhmaṇa, putto te dhammapālakumāro paññavā tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ aṭṭhārasannañca sippānaṃ nipphattiṃ patto, apica kho panekena aphāsukena jīvitakkhayaṃ patto, sabbe saṅkhārā aniccā, mā socitthā’’ ti āha. "
