507154,113,677,24,44,1,145,16,Rājagahanagarasmiñhi kenacideva karaṇīyena santhāgāre sannipatitassa mahājanassa majjhe eko puriso‘‘ ajja me maṅgalakiriyā atthī’’ ti uṭṭhāya agamāsi. 
507155,113,677,45,68,1,85,15,"Aparo tassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ ayaṃ‘ maṅgalan’ ti vatvāva gato, kiṃ etaṃ maṅgalaṃ nāmā’’ ti āha . "
