507483,113,804,41,116,1,312,48,"Rājā satiṃ paccupaṭṭhapetvā uṭṭhāya‘‘ mātula, mā bhāyi, ehī’’ ti pakkositvā āgataṃ‘‘ kosi nāma tvan’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ ahaṃ sāmi, jarā nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ jarāya viddho marissatīti kira maṃ porāṇā byākariṃsu, nissaṃsayaṃ ajja mayā maritabban’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ mātula, mā bhāyi, ehi pahāraṃ me bandhā’’ ti tena pahāramukhaṃ bandhāpetvā taṃ uyyojesi. "
507484,113,804,117,125,1,69,7,"Balavavedanā pavattiṃsu, itarehi ābhataṃ āhāraṃ paribhuñjituṃ nāsakkhi. "
507485,113,804,126,159,1,193,27,"Atha te āmantetvā‘‘ ajja ahaṃ marissāmi, tumhe pana sukhumālā aññaṃ kammaṃ katvā jīvituṃ na sakkhissatha, imaṃ vijjaṃ sikkhathā’’ ti ekaṃ vijjaṃ sikkhāpetvā te uyyojetvā tattheva jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇi. "
507486,113,804,160,166,1,53,6,Evaṃ añjanadeviṃ ṭhapetvā sabbeva vināsaṃ pāpuṇiṃsūti. 
