507601,113,875,2,7,1,18,2,[ 456]2. Juṇhajātakavaṇṇanā 
507602,113,876,2,15,1,104,12,Suṇohi mayhaṃ vacanaṃ {janindā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ānandattherena laddhavare ārabbha kathesi. 
507603,113,876,16,22,1,67,6,Paṭhamabodhiyañhi vīsati vassāni bhagavato anibaddhupaṭṭhākā ahesuṃ. 
507604,113,876,23,49,1,140,19,"Ekadā thero nāgasamālo, ekadā nāgito, ekadā upavāṇo, ekadā sunakkhatto, ekadā cundo, ekadā nando, ekadā sāgato, ekadā meghiyo bhagavantaṃ upaṭṭhahi. "
507605,113,876,50,87,1,225,27,"Athekadivasaṃ bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi‘‘ bhikkhave, idānimhi mahallako, ekacce bhikkhū‘ iminā maggena gacchāmā’ ti vutte aññena gacchanti, ekacce mayhaṃ pattacīvaraṃ bhūmiyaṃ nikkhipanti, nibaddhupaṭṭhākaṃ me ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ jānāthā’’ ti."
507606,113,876,88,117,1,151,18,"‘‘ Bhante, ahaṃ upaṭṭhahissāmi, ahaṃ upaṭṭhahissāmī’’ ti sirasi añjaliṃ katvā uṭṭhite sāriputtattherādayo‘‘ tumhākaṃ patthanā matthakaṃ pattā, alan’’ ti paṭikkhipi. "
507607,113,876,118,132,1,71,9,"Tato bhikkhū ānandattheraṃ‘‘ tvaṃ āvuso, upaṭṭhākaṭṭhānaṃ yācāhī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
507608,113,876,133,225,1,585,74,"Thero‘‘ sace me bhante, bhagavā attanā laddhacīvaraṃ na dassati, piṇḍapātaṃ na dassati, ekagandhakuṭiyaṃ vasituṃ na dassati, maṃ gahetvā nimantanaṃ na gamissati, sace pana bhagavā mayā gahitaṃ nimantanaṃ gamissati, sace ahaṃ tiroraṭṭhā tirojanapadā bhagavantaṃ daṭṭhuṃ āgataṃ parisaṃ āgatakkhaṇeyeva dassetuṃ labhissāmi , yadā me kaṅkhā uppajjati, tasmiṃ khaṇeyeva bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamituṃ labhissāmi, sace yaṃ bhagavā mama parammukhā dhammaṃ katheti, taṃ āgantvā mayhaṃ kathessati, evāhaṃ bhagavantaṃ upaṭṭhahissāmī’’ ti ime cattāro paṭikkhepe catasso ca āyācanāti aṭṭha vare yāci, bhagavāpissa adāsi. "
507609,113,877,2,9,1,59,7,So tato paṭṭhāya pañcavīsati vassāni nibaddhupaṭṭhāko ahosi. 
507610,113,877,10,44,1,320,28,"So pañcasu ṭhānesu etadagge ṭhapanaṃ patvā āgamasampadā, adhigamasampadā, pubbahetusampadā, attatthaparipucchāsampadā, titthavāsasampadā, yonisomanasikārasampadā, buddhūpanissayasampadāti imāhi sattahi sampadāhi samannāgato buddhassa santike aṭṭhavaradāyajjaṃ labhitvā buddhasāsane paññāto gaganamajjhe cando viya pākaṭo ahosi. "
507611,113,877,45,62,1,112,11,"Athekadivasaṃ bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, tathāgato ānandattheraṃ varadānena santappesī’’ ti. "
507612,113,877,63,115,1,224,33,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepāhaṃ ānandaṃ varena santappesiṃ, pubbepāhaṃ yaṃ yaṃ esa yāci, taṃ taṃ adāsiṃyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
507613,113,878,2,45,1,380,42,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa putto juṇhakumāro nāma hutvā takkasilāyaṃ sippaṃ uggahetvā ācariyassa anuyogaṃ datvā rattibhāge andhakāre ācariyassa gharā nikkhamitvā attano nivāsaṭṭhānaṃ vegena gacchanto aññataraṃ brāhmaṇaṃ bhikkhaṃ caritvā attano nivāsaṭṭhānaṃ gacchantaṃ apassanto bāhunā paharitvā tassa bhattapātiṃ bhindiṃ, brāhmaṇo patitvā viravi. "
507614,113,878,46,53,1,56,7,Kumāro kāruññena nivattitvā taṃ hatthe gahetvā uṭṭhāpesi. 
507615,113,878,54,72,1,74,11,"Brāhmaṇo‘‘ tayā, tāta, mama bhikkhābhājanaṃ bhinnaṃ, bhattamūlaṃ me dehī’’ ti āha. "
507616,113,878,73,112,1,235,32,"Kumāro‘‘ brāhmaṇa, na dānāhaṃ tava bhattamūlaṃ dātuṃ sakkomi, ahaṃ kho pana kāsikarañño putto juṇhakumāro nāma, mayi rajje patiṭṭhite āgantvā maṃ dhanaṃ yāceyyāsī’’ ti vatvā niṭṭhitasippo ācariyaṃ vanditvā bārāṇasiṃ gantvā pitu sippaṃ dassesi. "
507617,113,878,113,129,1,77,11,"Pitā‘‘ jīvantena me putto diṭṭho, rājabhūtampi naṃ passissāmī’’ ti rajje abhisiñci. "
507618,113,878,130,138,1,46,7,So juṇharājā nāma hutvā dhammena rajjaṃ kāresi. 
507619,113,878,139,165,1,190,22,Brāhmaṇo taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā‘‘ idāni mama bhattamūlaṃ āharissāmī’’ ti bārāṇasiṃ gantvā rājānaṃ alaṅkatanagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ karontameva disvā ekasmiṃ unnatappadese ṭhito hatthaṃ pasāretvā jayāpesi. 
507620,113,878,166,171,1,35,5,Atha naṃ rājā anoloketvāva atikkami. 
507621,113,878,172,180,1,73,8,Brāhmaṇo tena adiṭṭhabhāvaṃ ñatvā kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpento paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
507622,113,879,2,4,1,0,0,13.
507623,113,880,2,13,1,58,8,"‘ ‘ Suṇohi mayhaṃ vacanaṃ janinda, atthena juṇhamhi idhānupatto; "
507624,113,881,2,13,1,64,8,"Na brāhmaṇe addhike tiṭṭhamāne, gantabbamāhu dvipadinda seṭṭhā’’ ti. "
507625,113,882,2,18,1,106,13,"Tattha {juṇhamhī}ti mahārāja, tayi juṇhamhi ahaṃ ekena atthena idhānuppatto, na nikkāraṇā idhāgatomhīti dīpeti. "
507626,113,882,19,23,1,24,3,{Addhike}ti addhānaṃ āgate. 
507627,113,882,24,38,1,114,14,Gantabban ti taṃ addhikaṃ addhānamāgataṃ yācamānaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ anoloketvāva gantabbanti paṇḍitā na āhu na kathentīti. 
507628,113,883,2,11,1,75,9,Rājā tassa vacanaṃ sutvā hatthiṃ vajiraṅkusena niggahetvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
507629,113,884,2,4,1,0,0,14.
507630,113,885,2,13,1,56,8,"‘ ‘ Suṇomi tiṭṭhāmi vadehi brahme, yenāsi atthena idhānupatto; "
507631,113,886,2,15,1,67,10,"Kaṃ vā tvamatthaṃ mayi patthayāno, idhāgamo brahme tadiṅgha brūhī’’ ti. "
507632,113,887,2,7,1,32,4,Tattha {iṅghā}ti codanatthe nipāto. 
507633,113,888,2,11,1,75,9,Tato paraṃ brāhmaṇassa ca rañño ca vacanapaṭivacanavasena sesagāthā kathitā– 
