507638,113,893,2,16,1,61,11,"‘ ‘ Tapo nu te brāhmaṇa bhiṃsarūpo, mantā nu te brāhmaṇa cittarūpā; "
507639,113,894,2,14,1,61,11,"Yakkhā nu te assavā santi keci, atthaṃ vā me abhijānāsi kattaṃ. "
