507668,113,922,17,27,1,91,9,{Bhiṃsarūpo}ti kiṃ nu te brāhmaṇa balavarūpasīlācāraguṇasaṅkhātaṃ tapokammaṃ atthīti pucchati. 
507669,113,922,28,38,1,63,9,Mantā nu {te}ti udāhu vicitrarūpā sabbatthasādhakā mantā te atthi. 
507670,113,922,39,48,1,65,8,{Assavā}ti vacanakārakā icchiticchitadāyakā yakkhā vā te keci santi. 
507671,113,922,49,61,1,72,11,"Kattan ti kataṃ, udāhu tayā kataṃ kiñci mama atthaṃ abhijānāsīti pucchati. "
507672,113,922,62,71,1,68,9,Saṅgatimattan ti samāgamamattaṃ tayā saddhiṃ pubbe mama āsīti vadati. 
507673,113,922,72,81,1,55,8,Jānato {me}ti jānantassa mama idaṃ paṭhamaṃ tava dassanaṃ. 
507674,113,922,82,88,1,34,5,Na {tābhijānāmī}ti na taṃ abhijānāmi. 
507675,113,922,89,93,1,39,4,Timīsikāyan ti bahalatimirāyaṃ rattiyaṃ. 
507676,113,922,94,163,1,410,54,"Te tattha {ṭhatvānā}ti te mayaṃ tasmiṃ aṃsena aṃsaṃ ghaṭṭitaṭṭhāne ṭhatvā vītisārayimha {tatthā}ti tasmiṃyeva ṭhāne saritabbayuttakaṃ kathaṃ vītisārayimha, ahaṃ‘‘ bhikkhābhājanaṃ me tayā bhinnaṃ, bhattamūlaṃ me dehī’’ ti avacaṃ, tvaṃ‘‘ idānāhaṃ tava bhattamūlaṃ dātuṃ na sakkomi, ahaṃ kho pana kāsikarañño putto juṇhakumāro nāma, mayi rajje patiṭṭhite āgantvā maṃ dhanaṃ yāceyyāsī’’ ti avacāti imaṃ sāraṇīyakathaṃ karimhāti āha. "
507677,113,922,164,177,1,104,10,"Sāyeva no {saṅgatimattamāsī}ti deva, amhākaṃ sāyeva aññamaññaṃ saṅgatimattamāsi, ekamuhuttikamahosīti dīpeti. "
507678,113,922,178,193,1,102,14,{Tato}ti tato pana taṃmuhuttikamittadhammato pacchā vā pure vā kadāci amhākaṃ saṅgati nāma na bhūtapubbā. 
507679,113,923,2,20,1,122,17,Na {paṇḍitā}ti brāhmaṇa paṇḍitā nāma taṃmuhuttikaṃ saṅgatiṃ vā cirakālasanthavāni vā yaṃ kiñci pubbe kataguṇaṃ vā na nāsenti. 
507680,113,923,21,25,1,19,2,{Bahumpī}ti bahukampi . 
507681,113,923,26,38,1,82,10,"{Akataññurūpā}ti yasmā bālā akataññusabhāvā, tasmā tesu bahumpi kataṃ nassatīti attho. "
507682,113,923,39,43,1,37,3,{Sukataññurūpā}ti suṭṭhu kataññusabhāvā. 
