507690,113,923,100,127,1,172,21,"‘‘ deva, kāsiraṭṭhādhipati yathā cando tārakānaṃ majjhe ṭhito tārakagaṇaparivuto pāṭipadato paṭṭhāya yāva puṇṇamā āpūrati, tathā ahampi ajja tayā dinnehi gāmavarādīhi āpūrāmī’’ ti. "
