507695,113,925,2,4,1,25,2,Juṇhajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
507696,113,927,2,7,1,28,2,[ 457]3. Dhammadevaputtajātakavaṇṇanā 
507697,113,928,2,13,1,104,10,Yasokaro {puññakarohamasmī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto devadattassa pathavipavesanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
507698,113,928,14,33,1,124,14,"Tadā hi bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, devadatto tathāgatena saddhiṃ paṭivirujjhitvā pathaviṃ paviṭṭho’’ ti. "
507699,113,928,34,87,1,264,35,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na idānevesa, bhikkhave, mama jinacakke pahāraṃ datvā pathaviṃ paviṭṭho, pubbepi dhammacakke pahāraṃ datvā pathaviṃ pavisitvā avīciparāyaṇo jātoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
507700,113,929,2,18,1,134,15,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāmāvacaradevaloke dhammo nāma devaputto hutvā nibbatti, devadatto adhammo nāma. "
507701,113,929,19,64,1,477,39,"Tesu dhammo dibbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍito dibbarathavaramabhiruyha accharāgaṇaparivuto manussesu sāyamāsaṃ bhuñjitvā attano attano gharadvāre sukhakathāya nisinnesu puṇṇamuposathadivase gāmanigamajanapadarājadhānīsu ākāse ṭhatvā‘‘ pāṇātipātādīhi dasahi akusalakammapathehi viramitvā mātupaṭṭhānadhammaṃ pitupaṭṭhānadhammaṃ tividhasucaritadhammañca pūretha , evaṃ saggaparāyaṇā hutvā mahantaṃ yasaṃ anubhavissathā’’ ti manusse dasa kusalakammapathe samādapento jambudīpaṃ padakkhiṇaṃ karoti. "
507702,113,929,65,82,1,111,13,Adhammo pana devaputto‘‘ pāṇaṃ hanathā’’ tiādinā nayena dasa akusalakammapathe samādapento jambudīpaṃ vāmaṃ karoti. 
507703,113,929,83,90,1,38,6,Atha tesaṃ ākāse rathā sammukhā ahesuṃ. 
507704,113,929,91,120,1,124,19,"Atha nesaṃ parisā‘‘ tumhe kassa, tumhe kassā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ mayaṃ dhammassa, mayaṃ adhammassā’’ ti vatvā maggā okkamitvā dvidhā jātā. "
507705,113,929,121,149,1,146,20,"Dhammopi adhammaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ samma, tvaṃ adhammo, ahaṃ dhammo, maggo mayhaṃ anucchaviko, tava rathaṃ okkāmetvā mayhaṃ maggaṃ dehī’’ ti paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
507706,113,930,2,4,1,0,0,26.
507707,113,931,2,9,1,54,5,"‘ ‘ Yasokaro puññakarohamasmi, sadātthuto samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ; "
507708,113,932,2,13,1,62,8,"Maggāraho devamanussapūjito, dhammo ahaṃ dehi adhamma maggan’’ ti. "
507709,113,933,2,8,1,48,5,Tattha {yasokaro}ti ahaṃ devamanussānaṃ yasadāyako. 
507710,113,933,9,12,1,23,3,Dutiyapadepi eseva nayo. 
507711,113,933,13,18,1,37,4,{Sadātthuto}ti sadā thuto niccapasattho. 
