507964,113,1084,158,189,1,299,25,"So sīsaṃ parāmasi, taṃ khaṇaññevassa gihiliṅgaṃ antaradhāyi, surattadupaṭṭaṃ nivatthameva, vijjulatāsadisaṃ kāyabandhanaṃ baddhameva, alattakapāṭalavaṇṇaṃ uttarāsaṅgacīvaraṃ ekaṃsaṃ katameva, meghavaṇṇaṃ paṃsukūlacīvaraṃ dakkhiṇaaṃsakūṭe ṭhapitameva, bhamaravaṇṇo mattikāpatto vāmaaṃsakūṭe laggitova ahosi. "
507965,113,1084,190,198,1,71,8,So ākāse ṭhatvā dhammaṃ desetvā uppatitvā nandamūlakapabbhāreyeva otari. 
507966,113,1085,2,46,1,337,38,Aparopi kāsigāmeyeva kuṭumbiko āpaṇe nisinno ekaṃ purisaṃ attano bhariyaṃ ādāya gacchantaṃ disvā taṃ uttamarūpadharaṃ itthiṃ indriyāni bhinditvā oloketvā puna cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ lobho vaḍḍhamāno maṃ apāyesu khipissatī’’ ti saṃviggamānaso vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā paccekabodhiñāṇaṃ nibbattetvā ākāse ṭhito dhammaṃ desetvā nandamūlakapabbhārameva gato. 
507967,113,1086,2,9,1,66,7,Aparepi kāsigāmavāsinoyeva dve pitāputtā ekato maggaṃ paṭipajjiṃsu. 
507968,113,1086,10,15,1,34,5,Aṭavīmukhe pana corā uṭṭhitā honti. 
507969,113,1086,16,56,1,286,33,"Te pitāputte labhitvā puttaṃ gahetvā‘‘ dhanaṃ āharitvā tava puttaṃ gaṇhā’’ ti pitaraṃ vissajjenti, dve bhātaro labhitvā kaniṭṭhaṃ gahetvā jeṭṭhaṃ vissajjenti, ācariyantevāsike labhitvā ācariyaṃ gahetvā antevāsikaṃ vissajjenti, antevāsiko sippalobhena dhanaṃ āharitvā ācariyaṃ gaṇhitvā gacchati. "
507970,113,1086,57,110,1,227,36,"Atha te pitāputtāpi tattha corānaṃ uṭṭhitabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ tvaṃ maṃ‘ pitā’ ti mā vada, ahampi taṃ‘ putto’ ti na vakkhāmī’’ ti katikaṃ katvā corehi gahitakāle‘‘ tumhe aññamaññaṃ kiṃ hothā’’ ti puṭṭhā‘‘ na kiñci homā’’ ti sampajānamusāvādaṃ kariṃsu. "
507971,113,1086,111,150,1,284,34,"Tesu aṭavito nikkhamitvā sāyaṃ nhāyitvā ṭhitesu putto attano sīlaṃ sodhento taṃ musāvādaṃ disvā‘‘ idaṃ pāpaṃ vaḍḍhamānaṃ maṃ apāyesu khipissati, imaṃ kilesaṃ niggaṇhissāmī’’ ti vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā paccekabodhiñāṇaṃ nibbattetvā ākāse ṭhito pitu dhammaṃ desetvā nandamūlakapabbhārameva gato. "
507972,113,1087,2,9,1,59,7,Aparopi kāsigāmeyeva pana eko gāmabhojako māghātaṃ kārāpesi. 
507973,113,1087,10,32,1,134,16,"Atha naṃ balikammakāle mahājano sannipatitvā āha‘‘ sāmi, mayaṃ migasūkarādayo māretvā yakkhānaṃ balikammaṃ karissāma, balikammakālo eso’’ ti. "
507974,113,1087,33,40,1,73,7,Tumhākaṃ pubbe karaṇaniyāmeneva karothāti manussā bahuṃ pāṇātipātamakaṃsu. 
507975,113,1087,41,75,1,257,29,So bahuṃ macchamaṃsaṃ disvā‘‘ ime manussā ettake pāṇe mārentā mamevekassa vacanena mārayiṃsū’’ ti kukkuccaṃ katvā vātapānaṃ nissāya ṭhitakova vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā paccekabodhiñāṇaṃ nibbattetvā ākāse ṭhito mahājanassa dhammaṃ desetvā nandamūlakapabbhārameva gato. 
507976,113,1088,2,36,1,174,22,"Aparopi kāsiraṭṭheyeva gāmabhojako majjavikkayaṃ vāretvā‘‘ sāmi, pubbe imasmiṃ kāle surāchaṇo nāma hoti, kiṃ karomā’’ ti mahājanena vutto‘‘ tumhākaṃ porāṇakaniyāmeneva karothā’’ ti āha. "
507977,113,1088,37,52,1,125,15,Manussā chaṇaṃ katvā suraṃ pivitvā kalahaṃ karontā hatthapāde bhañjitvā sīsaṃ bhinditvā kaṇṇe chinditvā bahudaṇḍena bajjhiṃsu. 
507978,113,1088,53,69,1,79,12,Gāmabhojako te disvā cintesi‘‘ mayi ananujānante ime imaṃ dukkhaṃ na vindeyyun’’ ti. 
507979,113,1088,70,94,1,183,20,So ettakena kukkuccaṃ katvā vātapānaṃ nissāya ṭhitakova vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā paccekabodhiñāṇaṃ nibbattetvā‘‘ appamattā hothā’’ ti ākāse ṭhatvā dhammaṃ desetvā nandamūlakapabbhārameva gato. 
