508062,113,1148,13,59,1,425,38,"Ekadivasañhi dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitā bhikkhū‘‘ āvuso, sace dasabalo agāraṃ ajjhāvasissa, sakalacakkavāḷagabbhe cakkavattirājā abhavissa sattaratanasamannāgato caturiddhīhi samiddho parosahassaputtaparivāro , so evarūpaṃ sirivibhavaṃ pahāya kāmesu dosaṃ disvā aḍḍharattasamaye channasahāyova kaṇṭakamāruyha nikkhamitvā anomanadītīre pabbajitvā chabbassāni dukkarakārikaṃ katvā sammāsambodhiṃ patto’’ ti satthu guṇakathaṃ kathayiṃsu. "
