508287,113,1273,2,7,1,20,2,[ 462]8. Saṃvarajātakavaṇṇanā 
508288,113,1274,2,15,1,98,12,Jānanto no {mahārājā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ossaṭṭhavīriyaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
508289,113,1274,16,94,1,656,66,"So kira sāvatthivāsī kulaputto satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā pabbajitvā laddhūpasampado ācariyupajjhāyavattaṃ pūrento ubhayāni pātimokkhāni paguṇāni katvā paripuṇṇapañcavasso kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā‘‘ araññe vasissāmī’’ ti ācariyupajjhāye āpucchitvā kosalaraṭṭhe ekaṃ paccantagāmaṃ gantvā tattha iriyāpathe pasannamanussehi paṇṇasālaṃ katvā upaṭṭhiyamāno vassaṃ upagantvā yuñjanto ghaṭento vāyamanto accāraddhena vīriyena temāsaṃ kammaṭṭhānaṃ bhāvetvā obhāsamattampi uppādetuṃ asakkonto cintesi‘‘ addhā ahaṃ satthārā desitesu catūsu puggalesu padaparamo, kiṃ me araññavāsena, jetavanaṃ gantvā tathāgatassa rūpasiriṃ passanto madhuradhammadesanaṃ suṇanto vītināmessāmī’’ ti. "
508290,113,1274,95,212,1,683,84,"So vīriyaṃ ossajitvā tato nikkhanto anupubbena jetavanaṃ gantvā ācariyupajjhāyehi ceva sandiṭṭhasambhattehi ca āgamanakāraṇaṃ puṭṭho tamatthaṃ kathetvā tehi‘‘ kasmā evamakāsī’’ ti garahitvā satthu santikaṃ netvā‘‘ kiṃ, bhikkhave, anicchamānaṃ bhikkhuṃ ānayitthā’’ ti vutte‘‘ ayaṃ, bhante, vīriyaṃ ossajitvā āgato’’ ti ārocite satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kirā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ kasmā bhikkhu vīriyaṃ ossaji, imasmiñhi sāsane nibbīriyassa kusītapuggalassa aggaphalaṃ arahattaṃ nāma natthi, āraddhavīriyā imaṃ dhammaṃ ārādhenti, tvaṃ kho pana pubbe vīriyavā ovādakkhamo, teneva kāraṇena bārāṇasirañño puttasatassa sabbakaniṭṭho hutvāpi paṇḍitānaṃ ovāde ṭhatvā setacchattaṃ pattosī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
508291,113,1275,2,13,1,96,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente saṃvarakumāro nāma puttasatassa sabbakaniṭṭho ahosi. 
508292,113,1275,14,27,1,78,9,Rājā ekekaṃ puttaṃ‘‘ sikkhitabbayuttakaṃ sikkhāpethā’’ ti ekekassa amaccassa adāsi. 
508293,113,1275,28,38,1,93,10,Saṃvarakumārassa ācariyo amacco bodhisatto ahosi paṇḍito byatto rājaputtassa pituṭṭhāne ṭhito. 
508294,113,1275,39,44,1,45,5,Amaccā sikkhitasippe rājaputte rañño dassesuṃ. 
508295,113,1275,45,50,1,35,5,Rājā tesaṃ janapadaṃ datvā uyyojesi. 
508296,113,1275,51,72,1,113,15,"Saṃvarakumāro sabbasippassa nipphattiṃ patvā bodhisattaṃ pucchi‘‘ tāta, sace maṃ pitā janapadaṃ peseti, kiṃ karomī’’ ti?"
508297,113,1275,73,104,1,168,22,"‘‘ Tāta, tvaṃ janapade dīyamāne taṃ aggahetvā‘ deva ahaṃ sabbakaniṭṭho, mayipi gate tumhākaṃ pādamūlaṃ tucchaṃ bhavissati, ahaṃ tumhākaṃ pādamūleyeva vasissāmī’ ti vadeyyāsī’’ ti. "
508298,113,1275,105,124,1,100,13,"Athekadivasaṃ rājā saṃvarakumāraṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ pucchi‘‘ kiṃ tāta, sippaṃ te niṭṭhitan’’ ti?"
508299,113,1275,125,133,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, devā’’ ti."
508300,113,1275,134,142,1,26,4,‘‘ Tuyhampi janapadaṃ demī’’ ti.
508301,113,1275,143,157,1,68,8,"‘‘ Deva tumhākaṃ pādamūlaṃ tucchaṃ bhavissati, pādamūleyeva vasissāmī’’ ti. "
508302,113,1275,158,167,1,34,5,Rājā tussitvā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
508303,113,1275,168,186,1,92,14,So tato paṭṭhāya rañño pādamūleyeva hutvā punapi bodhisattaṃ pucchi‘‘ tāta aññaṃ kiṃ karomī’’ ti?
508304,113,1275,187,197,1,40,6,‘‘ Tāta rājānaṃ ekaṃ purāṇuyyānaṃ yācāhī’’ ti. 
508305,113,1275,198,222,1,114,16,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti uyyānaṃ yācitvā tattha jātakehi pupphaphalehi nagare issarajanaṃ saṅgaṇhitvā puna‘‘ kiṃ karomī’’ ti pucchi.
508306,113,1275,223,236,1,64,8,"‘‘ Tāta, rājānaṃ āpucchitvā antonagare bhattavetanaṃ tvameva dehī’’ ti. "
508307,113,1275,237,269,1,306,31,"So tathā katvā antonagare kassaci kiñci ahāpetvā bhattavetanaṃ datvā puna bodhisattaṃ pucchitvā rājānaṃ viññāpetvā antonivesane dāsaporisānampi hatthīnampi assānampi balakāyassapi vattaṃ aparihāpetvā adāsi, tirojanapadehi āgatānaṃ dūtādīnaṃ nivāsaṭṭhānādīni vāṇijānaṃ suṅkanti sabbakaraṇīyāni attanāva akāsi. "
508308,113,1275,270,296,1,189,25,"Evaṃ so mahāsattassa ovāde ṭhatvā sabbaṃ antojanañca bahijanañca nāgare ca raṭṭhavāsino ca āgantuke ca āyavattane ca tena tena saṅgahavatthunā ābandhitvā saṅgaṇhi, sabbesaṃ piyo ahosi manāpo. "
