508550,113,1403,2,7,1,23,2,[ 465]2. Bhaddasālajātakavaṇṇanā 
508551,113,1404,2,14,1,90,11,Kā tvaṃ suddhehi {vatthehī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ñātatthacariyaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
508552,113,1404,15,28,1,125,12,"Sāvatthiyañhi anāthapiṇḍikassa nivesane pañcannaṃ bhikkhusatānaṃ nibaddhabhojanaṃ pavattati, tathā visākhāya ca kosalarañño ca. "
508553,113,1404,29,59,1,225,27,"Tattha pana kiñcāpi nānaggarasabhojanaṃ dīyati, bhikkhūnaṃ panettha koci vissāsiko natthi, tasmā bhikkhū rājanivesane na bhuñjanti, bhattaṃ gahetvā anāthapiṇḍikassa vā visākhāya vā aññesaṃ vā vissāsikānaṃ gharaṃ gantvā bhuñjanti. "
508554,113,1404,60,116,1,263,35,"Rājā ekadivasaṃ paṇṇākāraṃ āhaṭaṃ‘‘ bhikkhūnaṃ dethā’’ ti bhattaggaṃ pesetvā‘‘ bhattagge bhikkhū natthī’’ ti vutte‘‘ kahaṃ gatā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ attano vissāsikagehesu nisīditvā bhuñjantī’’ ti sutvā bhuttapātarāso satthu santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ bhante, bhojanaṃ nāma kiṃ paraman’’ ti pucchi. "
508555,113,1404,117,125,1,76,7,"Vissāsaparamaṃ mahārāja, kañjikamattakampi vissāsikena dinnaṃ madhuraṃ hotīti. "
508556,113,1404,126,134,1,50,7,"Bhante, kena pana saddhiṃ bhikkhūnaṃ vissāso hotīti?"
508557,113,1404,135,146,1,37,6,"‘‘ Ñātīhi vā sekkhakulehi vā, mahārājā’’ ti. "
508558,113,1404,147,170,1,128,17,"Tato rājā cintesi‘‘ ekaṃ sakyadhītaraṃ ānetvā aggamahesiṃ karissāmi, evaṃ mayā saddhiṃ bhikkhūnaṃ ñātake viya vissāso bhavissatī’’ ti. "
508559,113,1404,171,193,1,126,17,"So uṭṭhāyāsanā attano nivesanaṃ gantvā kapilavatthuṃ dūtaṃ pesesi‘‘ dhītaraṃ me detha, ahaṃ tumhehi saddhiṃ ñātibhāvaṃ icchāmī’’ ti. "
508560,113,1405,2,39,1,201,26,"Sākiyā dūtavacanaṃ sutvā sannipatitvā mantayiṃsu‘‘ mayaṃ kosalarañño āṇāpavattiṭṭhāne vasāma, sace dārikaṃ na dassāma, mahantaṃ veraṃ bhavissati, sace dassāma, kulavaṃso no bhijjissati, kiṃ nu kho kātabban’’ ti. "
508561,113,1405,40,44,1,20,4,Atha ne mahānāmo āha–
