508924,113,1540,15,23,1,78,8,Eko kira sāvatthivāsī brāhmaṇo aciravatītīre khettakaraṇatthāya araññaṃ koṭesi. 
508925,113,1540,24,70,1,223,31,"Satthā tassa upanissayaṃ disvā sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pavisanto maggā okkamma tena saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ kiṃ karosi brāhmaṇā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ khettaṭṭhānaṃ koṭāpemi bho, gotamā’’ ti vutte‘‘ sādhu, brāhmaṇa, kammaṃ karohī’’ ti vatvā agamāsi. "
