509527,113,1839,2,7,1,17,2,[ 474]1. Ambajātakavaṇṇanā 
509528,113,1840,2,17,1,86,11,Ahāsi me ambaphalāni {pubbe}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
509529,113,1840,18,50,1,220,27,"Devadatto hi‘‘ ahaṃ buddho bhavissāmi, mayhaṃ samaṇo gotamo neva ācariyo na upajjhāyo’’ ti ācariyaṃ paccakkhāya jhānaparihīno saṅghaṃ bhinditvā anupubbena sāvatthiṃ āgacchanto bahijetavane pathaviyā vivare dinne avīciṃ pāvisi. "
509530,113,1840,51,71,1,131,14,"Tadā bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, devadatto ācariyaṃ paccakkhāya mahāvināsaṃ patto, avīcimahāniraye nibbatto’’ ti. "
509531,113,1840,72,116,1,200,27,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepi devadatto ācariyaṃ paccakkhāya mahāvināsaṃ pattoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
509532,113,1841,2,11,1,86,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente tassa purohitakulaṃ ahivātarogena vinassi. 
509533,113,1841,12,17,1,36,5,Ekova putto bhittiṃ bhinditvā palāto. 
509534,113,1841,18,43,1,184,21,So takkasilaṃ gantvā disāpāmokkhassācariyassa santike tayo vede ca avasesasippāni ca uggahetvā ācariyaṃ vanditvā nikkhanto‘‘ desacārittaṃ jānissāmī’’ ti caranto ekaṃ paccantanagaraṃ pāpuṇi. 
509535,113,1841,44,48,1,35,4,Taṃ nissāya mahācaṇḍālagāmako ahosi. 
509536,113,1841,49,61,1,89,11,"Tadā bodhisatto tasmiṃ gāme paṭivasati, paṇḍito byatto akāle phalaṃ gaṇhāpanamantaṃ jānāti. "
509537,113,1841,62,84,1,179,21,So pātova vuṭṭhāya kājaṃ ādāya tato gāmā nikkhimitvā araññe ekaṃ ambarukkhaṃ upasaṅkamitvā sattapadamatthake ṭhito taṃ mantaṃ parivattetvā ambarukkhaṃ ekena udakapasatena paharati. 
509538,113,1841,85,107,1,192,19,"Rukkhato taṅkhaṇaññeva purāṇapaṇṇāni patanti, navāni uṭṭhahanti, pupphāni pupphitvā patanti, ambaphalāni uṭṭhāya muhutteneva paccitvā madhurāni ojavantāni dibbarasasadisāni hutvā rukkhato patanti. "
509539,113,1841,108,121,1,108,13,Mahāsatto tāni uccinitvā yāvadatthaṃ khāditvā kājaṃ pūrāpetvā gehaṃ gantvā tāni vikkiṇitvā puttadāraṃ posesi. 
509540,113,1842,2,77,1,484,59,"So brāhmaṇakumāro mahāsattaṃ akāle ambapakkāni āharitvā vikkiṇantaṃ disvā‘‘ nissaṃsayena tehi mantabalena uppannehi bhavitabbaṃ, imaṃ purisaṃ nissāya idaṃ anagghamantaṃ labhissāmī’’ ti cintetvā mahāsattassa ambāni āharaṇaniyāmaṃ pariggaṇhanto tathato ñatvā tasmiṃ araññato anāgateyeva tassa gehaṃ gantvā ajānanto viya hutvā tassa bhariyaṃ‘‘ kuhiṃ ayyo, ācariyo’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ araññaṃ gato’’ ti vutte taṃ āgataṃ āgamayamānova ṭhatvā āgacchantaṃ disvā hatthato pacchiṃ gahetvā āharitvā gehe ṭhapesi. "
509541,113,1842,78,83,1,35,5,Mahāsatto taṃ oloketvā bhariyaṃ āha–
509542,113,1842,84,103,1,81,12,"‘‘ bhadde, ayaṃ māṇavo mantatthāya āgato, tassa hatthe manto nassati, asappuriso eso’’ ti. "
509543,113,1842,104,124,1,120,16,Māṇavopi‘‘ ahaṃ imaṃ mantaṃ ācariyassa upakārako hutvā labhissāmī’’ ti cintetvā tato paṭṭhāya tassa gehe sabbakiccāni karoti. 
509544,113,1842,125,139,1,90,10,"Dārūni āharati, vīhiṃ koṭṭeti, bhattaṃ pacati, dantakaṭṭhamukhadhovanādīni deti, pādaṃ dhovati. "
509545,113,1843,2,23,1,125,16,"Ekadivasaṃ mahāsattena‘‘ tāta māṇava, mañcapādānaṃ me upadhānaṃ dehī’’ ti vutte aññaṃ apassitvā sabbarattiṃ ūrumhi ṭhapetvā nisīdi. "
509546,113,1843,24,29,1,45,5,Aparabhāge mahāsattassa bhariyā puttaṃ vijāyi. 
509547,113,1843,30,34,1,39,4,Tassā pasūtikāle parikammaṃ sabbamakāsi. 
509548,113,1843,35,66,1,163,24,"Sā ekadivasaṃ mahāsattaṃ āha‘‘ sāmi, ayaṃ māṇavo jātisampanno hutvā mantatthāya amhākaṃ veyyāvaccaṃ karoti, etassa hatthe manto tiṭṭhatu vā mā vā, detha tassa mantan’’ ti. "
509549,113,1843,67,80,1,53,8,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā tassa mantaṃ datvā evamāha–
509550,113,1843,81,136,1,278,40,"‘‘ tāta, anagghoyaṃ manto, tava imaṃ nissāya mahālābhasakkāro bhavissati, raññā vā rājamahāmattena vā‘ ko te ācariyo’ ti puṭṭhakāle mā maṃ nigūhittho, sace hi‘ caṇḍālassa me santikā manto gahito’ ti lajjanto‘ brāhmaṇamahāsālo me ācariyo’ ti kathessasi, imassa mantassa phalaṃ na labhissasī’’ ti. "
509551,113,1843,137,167,1,198,25,"So‘‘ kiṃ kāraṇā taṃ nigūhissāmi, kenaci puṭṭhakāle tumheyeva kathessāmī’’ ti vatvā taṃ vanditvā caṇḍālagāmato nikkhamitvā mantaṃ vīmaṃsitvā anupubbena bārāṇasiṃ patvā ambāni vikkiṇitvā bahuṃ dhanaṃ labhi. "
509552,113,1844,2,10,1,65,8,Athekadivasaṃ uyyānapālo tassa hatthato ambaṃ kiṇitvā rañño adāsi. 
509553,113,1844,11,28,1,71,11,"Rājā taṃ paribhuñjitvā‘‘ kuto samma, tayā evarūpaṃ ambaṃ laddhan’’ ti pucchi. "
509554,113,1844,29,40,1,67,9,"Deva, eko māṇavo akālaambaphalāni ānetvā vikkiṇāti, tato me gahitanti. "
509555,113,1844,41,55,1,58,10,Tena hi‘‘ ito paṭṭhāya idheva ambāni āharatū’’ ti naṃ vadehīti. 
509556,113,1844,56,59,1,14,3,So tathā akāsi. 
509557,113,1844,60,66,1,46,6,Māṇavopi tato paṭṭhāya ambāni rājakulaṃ harati. 
509558,113,1844,67,85,1,102,14,Atha raññā‘‘ upaṭṭhaha man’’ ti vutte rājānaṃ upaṭṭhahanto bahuṃ dhanaṃ labhitvā anukkamena vissāsiko jāto. 
509559,113,1844,86,120,1,164,26,"Atha naṃ ekadivasaṃ rājā pucchi‘‘ māṇava, kuto akāle evaṃ vaṇṇagandharasasampannāni ambāni labhasi, kiṃ te nāgo vā supaṇṇo vā devo vā koci deti, udāhu mantabalaṃ etan’’ ti?"
509560,113,1844,121,141,1,69,13,"‘‘ Na me mahārāja, koci deti, anaggho pana me manto atthi, tasseva balan’’ ti."
509561,113,1844,142,154,1,54,8,‘‘ Tena hi mayampi te ekadivasaṃ mantabalaṃ daṭṭhukāmā’’ ti.
509562,113,1844,155,165,1,24,4,"‘‘ Sādhu, deva, dassessāmī’’ ti. "
509563,113,1844,166,179,1,58,9,Rājā punadivase tena saddhiṃ uyyānaṃ gantvā‘‘ dassehī’’ ti āha. 
